DESCRIPTION:CATALYZE is an annual conference by the Comparative Medicine In
 stitute that seeks to equip faculty\, students and postdocs with the abilit
 y to bring their biomedical research ideas to market. This event will inclu
 de talks and panel discussions featuring NC State's Office of Research Comm
 ercialization and the North Carolina Biotechnology Center. Entrepreneur Nic
 ole Bell\, an author and the CEO of Galaxy Diagnostics\, will deliver the k
 eynote address.
