DESCRIPTION:Durham’s Alley Twenty Six is offering menu specials with cocktail pairings for Galentine’s and Valentine’s celebrations from Feb. 12-14. The menu includes:\nStarters\nOysters Deluxe (six) with Smoked Trout Roe\, Creme Fraiche and Chives; $42\nLittle Gem Lettuces with Herb Toasted Bread Crumbs\, Reggianito\, Boquerones\, Salt Cured Egg Yolk and Green Goddess Dressing; $15\nPaired with: Clearly Royale: a clarified milk punch of Conniption Navy Strength Gin\, dry Vermouth\, lemon and tea topped with Prosecco; $18\nEntree\nSurf and Turf For Two: a 16-ounce Chateaubriand\, Butter Poached Lobster Tail\, Mushroom Ragout\, Potato Puree and Chimichurri Sauce; $125\nPaired with Lover’s Rock: Copper and Kings American Brandy\, Mattei Cap Corse Rouge and Bitters; $18\nDessert\nChocolate Swirl Cheesecake with Whipped Cream and Mixed Berry Compote; $12\nPaired with Rose Colored Glasses with 1000 Piers Coastal Carolina Gin\, Strawberry\, Dolin Chamberyzette Strawberry Aperitif\, Lillet Rosé\, Nardini Bitter Aperitivo and Bitters; $16\nAlley Twenty Six is located at 320 E. Chapel Hill St.\, Durham. Info: alleytwentysix.com
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/valentines-at-alley-twenty-six/2026-03-06/
LOCATION:Alley Twenty Six\, 320 E Chapel Hill St\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
CATEGORIES:Food & Drink,Holiday,Special Offer,Valentine,Wines, Spirits, Beer and Cheer
