BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"UNC Chapel Hill": "https://calendar.unc.edu/event/paying-off-debt-while-building-wealth-2537"}
X-SOURCE-ID:unc_chapel_hill
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:In difficult economic times\, many people are struggling to jus
 t keep up with monthly bills\, let alone make progress on debt repayment. W
 hat suffers most is contributing to savings and investing goals. This sessi
 on will focus on developing financial plans and strategies to address the d
 ual goals of having a plan for paying off debt\, while also contributing to
  building personal wealth.\nThis session covers the basics (or essentials) 
 of each area and describes practical techniques that can help you to formul
 ate your own plan to manage your personal finances to organize a sensible d
 ebt repayment plan without sacrificing other financial goals.\n\n \n\nWorks
 hop Objectives:\n\n-Recognize the importance of a practical debt repayment 
 strategy\n-Understand the importance of setting and tracking short- and lon
 g-term financial goals\n-Learn how to set milestones to address debt repaym
 ent and savings\n-Be able to prioritize most effective use of disposable in
 come\n-Differentiate between saving and investing and when each makes sense
 \n\n \n\nClick on Carolina Talent registration link and select the “Request
 ” button to automatically enroll.
DTEND:20260306T180000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022131Z
DTSTART:20260306T170000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Paying off Debt While Building Wealth
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51375305056806
