X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Exhibits
DESCRIPTION:Join Ackland educators for a lively half-hour look at a small h
 andful of artworks. These engaging conversational tours offer a closer look
  at and new perspectives on works on view at the Museum. Today’s tour looks
  at Bill Bamberger: Boys Will Be Men. \nThis is a free\, walk-in event – no
  RSVP required. \nThis event is part of UNC–Chapel Hill’s Campus Life Exper
 ience (CLE) program. Students who attend can scan the QR code provided at t
 he event to receive CLE credit.
