DESCRIPTION:Parents and Families Services invites students to bring sibling
 s ages 7–17 to main campus for a special day designed just for them. PacKIN
  Action will give brothers\, sisters\, cousins and family friends a hands-o
 n look at college life through campus traditions and interactive activities
 . The day’s events will include an interactive campus scavenger hunt\, tie-
 dye shirt decorating\, s’mores with the mascots\, dinner at a dining hall a
 nd admission into the A cappella Showcase. Food and beverages are included 
 with registration.\n\nEach participant will receive a T-shirt\, swag bag\, 
 Pack Passport\, water bottle and lasting memories of the Wolfpack spirit. W
 hether it’s their first visit or a return trip\, every sibling will leave f
 eeling part of the Pack family.
