DESCRIPTION:The College of Design Fish Market will host Works in Progress o
 n March 6 from 6-11 p.m. at the Fish Market Gallery\, 133 Fayetteville St. 
 in Raleigh. Explore this year's exhibition lineup.\n\nWorks in Progress emp
 hasises the beauty of the unfinished and the process of creating. We will a
 ccept half-finished pieces\, sketches\, sketchbooks\, tools and materials f
 rom artists to show the diversity in artistic and design methods across NC 
 State students. We will have interactive elements that will allow guests to
  participate in the art-making process.\n\nParking is available at the Muni
 cipal Parking Deck\, 201 West Morgan St. in Raleigh.
