DESCRIPTION:Please join Engaged Defenders for Democracy for a Signs of Fasc
 ism event. We will meet at Peace &amp\; Justice Plaza in Chapel Hill (179 E
  Franklin Street) to raise awareness about elements of fascism that we are 
 seeing in our country today. We will hold signs written with signs of fasci
 sm spaced out about 25 feet apart along Franklin Street. This event is bein
 g held in collaboration the Community Church of Chapel Hill&#39\;s Day of S
 ervice.\nPlease choose one or two shifts. We are asking folks to commit to 
 holding a sign for 45 minutes (you can sign up for both shifts)\, arriving 
 at 9:30 am to get set up and holding your sign from 9:45-10:30 am\, or arri
 ving at 10:15 am and holding a sign from 10:30-11:15 am. Before or after yo
 ur shift\, we will have handouts to pass out to pedestrians with informatio
 n about how people can combat the fascism we see through specific actions.\
 n\nCheck in at Peace &amp\; Justice Plaza to get your sign and instructions
 . You will also receive an email with more detailed instructions closer to 
 the event. \n\nChildren are welcome but must be supervised by an adult at a
 ll times.\nLimited street parking available downtown - paid parking decks a
 re available. \n\nMore information here: <a href="https://www.google.com/ur
 l?q=https://parkonthehill.com/public-parking/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calenda
 r&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw00-Lq8EywXVWkCc2Kjtn02" target="_blank">https:/
 /parkonthehill.com/public-parking/</a> Carpooling or public transportation 
 encouraged.\n\nPlease join our Substack: <a href="https://www.google.com/ur
 l?q=https://substack.com/profile/115484101-engaged-defenders-4-democracy&am
 p\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw3y7Kv9RwiMPWcPPUFQih
 9k" target="_blank">https://substack.com/profile/115484101-engaged-defender
 s-4-democracy</a>\n\nFor more ED4D Mobilize Events: <a href="https://www.go
 ogle.com/url?q=https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/&amp\;sa
 =D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw1xqNbFip0P6DfK4plFB1D7" t
 arget="_blank">https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/</a>\n\n
 <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefende
 rsfordemocracy/event/902116/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\
 ;usg=AOvVaw2JJOI3jlT2wsN9JhoM8XaU" target="_blank">https://www.mobilize.us/
 engagedefendersfordemocracy/event/902116/</a>
