DESCRIPTION:Bring your family and friends to Town Creek on Saturday\, March
  7th\, and find out who is the Chunkey Champion. One of the oldest games in
  the Americas\, Chunkey was played for fun and to settle arguments. Learn t
 he history of this popular pastime while enjoying a few rounds for yourself
 . Proceeds benefit The Friends of Town Creek Indian Mound Inc.\, which supp
 orts programs at Town Creek Indian Mound State Historic Site. \n\nGames beg
 in at 10am\, 12pm\, and 2pm
