DESCRIPTION:How to join:\nYou will be asked to complete a brief Zoom regist
 ration at the time you log-in for the event.\n\nSharing stories and connect
 ing around our lived experiences in a vulnerable way is at the heart of pow
 erful\, connected conversations. But vulnerability sits differently for eac
 h of us depending on our identities and what our life experiences have been
 . Join us to explore and practice storytelling and vulnerability in a suppo
 rted training environment so you can leverage the impact of the stories you
  want to tell and elicit from others.\n\n*This session will be offered twic
 e - please choose the date/time that works best for you.*\n\nhttps://www.mo
 bilize.us/thenewconversationinitiative/event/876481/
LAST-MODIFIED:20251231T153840Z
LOCATION:Virtual event
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:[Deep Canvass Institute] Skills Session 2: Vulnerability & Honesty 
 in Story Exchange
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
