X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Downtown Durham Inc": "https://downtowndurham.com/event/luewwd-xx-luewwd-family-values/", "Motorco Music Hall": "https://motorcomusic.com/event/luewwd-xx/"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Downtown Durham Inc": "https://downtowndurham.com/event/luewwd-xx-luewwd-family-values/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:downtown_durham
X-SOURCE:Downtown Durham Inc, Motorco Music Hall
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260307T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260307T213000
DTSTAMP:20260306T165929
CREATED:20260224T154809Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260224T154809Z
UID:10227076-1772911800-1772919000@downtowndurham.com
SUMMARY:LUEWWD XX: LUEWWD Family Values
DESCRIPTION:The League of Upper Extremity Wrestling Women of Durham (LUEWWD\, pronounced “lewd”) will host its 20th theatrical and competitive arm wrestling fundraiser on Saturday\, March 7\, at Motorco Music Hall in Durham\, NC. The event begins at 7:30 p.m.\, with tickets available for $12 plus fees in advance and $20 at the door. For 16 years\, LUEWWD has brought the Durham community together through high-energy\, costumed arm wrestling competitions that raise critical funds for local causes. This milestone 20th event continues that tradition\, with all proceeds benefiting two organizations working to ensure community members have reliable access to food: Urban Community AgriNomics (UCAN) and PORCH Chapel Hill- Carrboro. \nThe March 7 showdown will feature eight costumed contestants\, each backed by a four-member entourage\, battling it out for four coveted titles: \nMadame Moneymaker: Awarded to the contestant who raises the most funds for LUEWWD’s nonprofit partners\nDurham Diva: Best costume and entourage\nQueen of the Losers: Winner of the losers’ bracket\nLUEWWD Champion: The overall arm wrestling victor
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/luewwd-xx-luewwd-family-values/
LOCATION:Motorco Music Hall\, 723 Rigsbee Ave\, Durham\, NC\, 27701
CATEGORIES:Community Engagement,Fundraiser
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://downtowndurham.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/26-002-LUE-LUEWWDXX_Social_ƒ-2.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="League of Upper Extremity Wrestling Women of Durham (LUEWWD)":MAILTO:noreply@facebookmail.com
GEO:36.0035224;-78.9003041
