DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260308T100000
SUMMARY:Interest Meeting for Acadia Nat’l Park Trip + Hike: North Cary P
 ark
DESCRIPTION:Triangle Hiking and Outdoors Group\nEver wanted to visit Acadi
 a National Park? Then this upcoming August event\, which includes beautifu
 l summit & coastal views\, a partial Solar Eclipse and the Perseids Meteor
  Shower\, is for you.\nJoin THOG and Wanderful Journeys at North Cary Park
  if you’re interested in hearing about this adventure through collaborat
 ion. Much like THOG's successful 2017 and 2024 Solar Eclipse trips\, this 
 Maine event will provide you with opportunities to have a once-in-a-lifeti
 me experience. We're also making sure that this road trip event will be en
 joyable for everyone\, drivers and passengers included.\nWe’ll meet by t
 he planters in front of the restrooms at the trailhead then gather nearby 
 to discuss the details of this August Trip. Your valuable input will help 
 us make this event a great one\, also.\nYou may need to arrive early. Park
 ing may be difficult to find if the park is busy.\nWe will introduce you t
 o the dates of the trip\, our itinerary\, accommodations & options\, costs
 \, and event highlights. We'll also answer questions and get your input.\n
 Afterwards we'll do a short hike of around 3-4 miles near and around the w
 ater just to enjoy the park and the views.\nIf you have any questions\, co
 mment below.\nSee you soon\,\nLarredo and Geniece
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/adventures/events/313223185/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260205T173043Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260205T173043Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
