DESCRIPTION:Come out for an afternoon of the best game out there with the best beer in town! Our buddies at Dungeons & Drafts are coming out to play 5e D&D as we enjoy drinks. They provide you with pre-made character sheets and dice so you don’t have to bring anything other than yourself (you’re welcome to bring your own dice of course!). Newbies welcome! Buy tickets at this link to ensure your spot! \nView on Facebook. \nHappens on the following Dates:\nJan 11\, 2026\, 12:00pm to 4:00pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)\nFeb 8\, 2026\, 12:00pm to 4:00pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)\nMar 8\, 2026\, 12:00pm to 4:00pm Timezone: Eastern Time (US & Canada)
