X-SOURCE-ID:unc_chapel_hill
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Exhibits
DESCRIPTION:Meet the artist and enjoy light refreshments at the exhibit rec
 eption for The Whimsical Naturalist at the North Carolina Botanical Garden 
 on Sunday\, March 8\, from 1-3 p.m.!\n\n \n\nIn this exhibit of original wa
 tercolors\, North Carolina artist Katie Crawford celebrates the rich biodiv
 ersity of the East Coast\, telling the story of interconnectedness between 
 species\, ecosystems\, and communities. Through portraits of native plants 
 and animals\, she uses anthropomorphism to shift perspectives and inspire v
 isitors to consider how we are connected to our environment and each other.
 \n\n \n\nThe reception takes place in and around the DeBerry Gallery\, in o
 ur main education center\, and is open to all.\n\n \n\nReminder: Sunday\, M
 arch 8 is the first day of Daylight Savings Time!
DTEND:20260308T190000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022131Z
DTSTART:20260308T170000Z
GEO:35.899603;-79.03247
LOCATION:North Carolina Botanical Garden
SEQUENCE:0
