UID:6a1ta0dagqudm7anhmknqrjoe4@google.com
CREATED:20250926T142442Z
DESCRIPTION:<span><br><br><br><p>Please join Engaged Defenders for Democrac
 y on Mondays from 7:30-9 at the corner of Franklin St &amp\; Elliott Rd in 
 Chapel Hill for a weekly\, peaceful\, nonpartisan protest and call to actio
 n. Free parking at the Church of Reconciliation\, 110 N Elliott Rd.</p><p>A
 cross the political spectrum\, Americans are disillusioned by leaders who p
 ut power over people. We gather to build community\, spark hope\, and inspi
 re action.</p><p>Bring a friend. Bring a sign. Speak up for immigrant right
 s\, free speech\, healthcare\, social security\, the environment\, the Cons
 titution and the rule of law\, reproductive freedom\, job and funding cuts\
 , and the many\, many other issues close to our hearts. Bonus points for si
 gns that encourage others to move beyond honking and help turn awareness in
 to action.  We often hand out fliers to stopped cars &amp\; pedestrians wit
 h information about relevant actions folks can take to support their commun
 ity and defend democracy. We also have a Signal chat for regular attenders.
  If you are interested in either of these opportunities\, ask around for We
 ndy.</p><p>This will be a POSITIVE and nonviolent demonstration. We are her
 e to protect our democracy. We are standing up for what we believe in. We w
 ant to inspire people to join us and grow our movement!</p><p>Please bring 
 positive signs supporting the movement and resisting what is happening in o
 ur country!</p><p>Please no mocking signs\, no swastikas</p><p>We are excit
 ed to see you there and stand together for our country!</p><p>See you every
  Monday afternoon engaging drivers in Chapel Hill!</p><p>Please join our Su
 bstack:<span> </span><a href="https://substack.com/profile/115484101-engage
 d-defenders-4-democracy">https://substack.com/profile/115484101-engaged-def
 enders-4-democracy</a></p><p>For more ED4D Mobilize Events:<span> </span><a
  href="https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/">https://www.mo
 bilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/</a></p><a href="https://www.mobilize
 .us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/event/881591/">https://www.mobilize.us/enga
 gedefendersfordemocracy/event/881591/</a></span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260306T223156Z
LOCATION:East Franklin Street & South Elliott Road\, Chapel Hill\, NC\, 275
 14
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Mobilization Mondays: Chapel Hill (mornings)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
