CATEGORIES:Student Life
DESCRIPTION:Join the Adopted Students Union for Roots and Routes\, a March 
 9 event that will be all about reflection and reconnection. We encourage pa
 rticipants to fully embrace where they came from and to create a visual or 
 mood board that offers a glimpse into who they are and what represents thei
 r “lost culture.” The goal is to foster a judgment-free space where everyon
 e feels comfortable expressing themselves and reconnecting with parts of th
 eir identity. Please create a physical or digital visual/mood board before 
 our March 9 event. During the event\, you can share your board. If you'd ju
 st like to visit and connect with others without creating a mood board\, yo
 u can do so as well.\n\nFree snacks will be provided. With St. Patrick’s Da
 y right around the corner\, you’ll also get to build your own “luck bag" an
 d decorate it with markers and other craft supplies.
DTEND:20260310T000000Z
