DESCRIPTION:Social media doesn't have to feel like a second full-time job.
  Join us for Social Media Made Simple\, led by the always dynamic Kim Kaid
  of Kaid Marketing. Kim brings the perfect mix of strategy\, creativity\, 
 and real-world practicality. (and our attendees consistently rave about he
 r sessions) In this interactive workshop\, you'll learn: Which platforms a
 ctually make sense for your business (hint: not all of them) How to create
  eye-catching graphics using simple\, customizable templates What to post\
 , when to post\, and how to stay consistent without burning out Kim will b
 reak it all down in a way that's current\, clear\, and immediatey actionab
 le. You'll leave with practical tools\, renewed confidence\, and a realist
 ic plan that makes social media work for your business... not the other wa
 y around. If you've ever thought "I know I should be doing more online\, b
 ut I don't know where to start\," this class is for you.
