LAST-MODIFIED:20260212T135440Z
UID:119319-1773138600-1773142200@naturalsciences.org
SUMMARY:Art Outdoors: Nature Wands
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we explore art outdoors\, mixing natural materials with traditional art disciplines\, testing new nature-based art techniques\, and using inspiration from nature to create artistic masterpieces. \nEach day will feature a different outdoor art activity – today’s activity is creating nature wands! Join us as we use natural materials to make a wand to take along on your magical outdoor explorations! \nThis drop-in program is designed for kids ages 7 and under and occurs outdoors from 10:30am – 11:30am at the picnic tables below the Nature PlaySpace. All children must be accompanied by an adult. Come dressed for the weather and prepared to get messy! Art Outdoors is a free program\, with a suggested donation of $5/child. Make your donation here. For more information\, contact prairieridge@naturalsciences.org.
URL:https://naturalsciences.org/calendar/event/art-outdoors-nature-mosaics-2-2/
LOCATION:Prairie Ridge\, 1671 Gold Star Drive\, Raleigh\, NC\, 27607\, United States
CATEGORIES:Children,Outdoor Experiences,Walk-up Programs
