X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: All Things AI": "https://www.meetup.com/all-things-ai-live/events/313490155/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_all_things_ai
X-SOURCE:Meetup: All Things AI
UID:event_313490155@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260307T022535Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260310T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260310T130000
SUMMARY:Lunch and Learn: The Path to Becoming AI-First: An Operator’s Pl
 aybook
DESCRIPTION:All Things AI (Live)\nWhat happens when a recruiting operator 
 — not a software engineer — decides to rebuild his company around AI?\
 n\nIn this live lunch & learn session\, James Horne\, Director of Delivery
  at Axiom Path\, shares how his team built 25+ AI automations and digital 
 employees that now operate alongside human recruiters — screening candid
 ates\, managing workflows\, and turning 21\,000+ historical recruiting not
 es into a searchable knowledge system.\n\nJames will demonstrate a live vo
 ice AI built to talk about...itself and it's role in Axiom Path and their 
 AI Transformation.\n\nThis session explores what it really means to become
  AI-first: starting with process\, increasing leverage\, and learning how 
 to manage digital employees alongside human employees.\n\nThis is not a co
 ding talk. It’s an operator’s blueprint.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/all-things-ai-live/events/313490155/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260223T135616Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260223T135616Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
