DESCRIPTION:The 12th annual UNC Cleantech Summit will take place at the UNC
  Friday Conference Center on March 9 – 10\, 2026. The two-day event will br
 ing together professionals in business\, government\, and academia from acr
 oss the Southeast and around the world for discussion\, workshops\, mentori
 ng\, and networking to foster leadership and growth in the Southeast’s clea
 ntech economy. The Summit convenes more than 1\,000 attendees and is the la
 rgest event of its kind by a university in the United States. Co-hosted by 
 the UNC Institue for the Environment and the Ackerman Center for Excellence
  in Sustainability at the Kenan-Flagler Business School.\n\n \n\nRegister h
 ere: https://web.cvent.com/event/dc0e55ed-323b-4ce9-bb78-8699d3e904f3/summa
 ry?RefId=UNC%20Website
