UID:2c69j6fvo7a4hf0rij8km2v48v@google.com
CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20260104T011450Z
DESCRIPTION:REGISTER HERE: <a href="https://righttobe.org/events/stand-up-a
 gainst-street-harassment-44/">https://righttobe.org/events/stand-up-against
 -street-harassment-44/</a><br><br><p>How can we take action if we don’t kno
 w what to do? Right To Be is offering this free\, one-hour\, interactive tr
 aining to train people on how to safely intervene when you witness street h
 arassment — or experience it yourself. During this training you’ll learn a 
 clear\, adaptable\, and expert-approved set of tools that have been proven 
 to reduce the prevalence of street harassment: Right To Be’s 5Ds of bystand
 er intervention.</p><p>We’ll start by deepening our understanding of street
  harassment and its impact. Then\, we’ll talk through five strategies for i
 ntervention: distract\, delegate\, document\, delay\, and direct\; and how 
 to prioritize your own safety while intervening. We’ll also talk about what
  to do if you’re worried the violence will turn on you and how to avoid esc
 alating the situation. Then\, we’ll talk about what to do if you experience
  harassment and give you tools to safely get your power back.</p><p>We’ll h
 ave time at the end for practice. Exit polls show 98.8% of attendees leave 
 the training feeling like there is at least one thing they can do the next 
 time they witness harassment.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260104T011450Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Right to Be's Stand Up Against Street Harassment
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
