DESCRIPTION:<span><p>Come join Engaged Defenders for Democracy as we meet o
 n Wednesdays from 3:30-5pm at American Tobacco Trail Bridge over I-40. Loca
 tion: AMC Streets of Southpoint 8030 Renaissance Pkwy Durham\, NC 27713. Pa
 rking lots are behind Southpoint Mall near the AMC theater or in the parkin
 g lot of Roses lot on Hwy 54. Go behind Southpoint Mall to the AMC theater 
 parking lot. Walk towards Hwy 40 and look for entrance to the trail. It is 
 a 4-minute walk. You also can park at Rose's\, 105 W NC. Hwy 54 27713. The 
 walk to the bridge from Roses is a 4-minute walk.</p><p>We will have a big 
 sign. If you bring signs\, please make sure they are positive and show what
  we are fighting for: "Freedom 4 All" "Protect Free Speech." Please bring A
 merican flags to wave as well.</p><p>See you there every Wednesday! Thanks 
 activism warriors!</p><p>Please join our Substack:<span> </span><a href="ht
 tps://substack.com/profile/115484101-engaged-defenders-4-democracy">https:/
 /substack.com/profile/115484101-engaged-defenders-4-democracy</a></p><p>For
