 ngagedefendersfordemocracy/">https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemo
 cracy/</a></p><p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocra
 cy/event/842871/">https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/event
 /842871/</a> </p></span>
