BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Durham Resistance": "https://durhamresistance.com/calendar"}
X-SOURCE-ID:durham_resistance_4
X-SOURCE:Durham Resistance
URL:https://durhamresistance.com/calendar
DTSTART:20260311T220000Z
DTEND:20260312T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022545Z
UID:2g8c5o60cro8bc4sgg53t26gpd@google.com
CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20260122T231635Z
DESCRIPTION:Link to join: https://www.mobilize.us/join/47683001/1:998e56654
 00e92aaf4fcfa1f230105583e6d8000ae6b908bd4a99cce24f41ad1/\n\nJoin Swing Left
  for a Ground Truth phone bank—designed to fix what’s broken in Democratic 
 organizing. We’re launching an innovative new program that will revolutioni
 ze how we connect with voters over the phone. \n\nOur goal: to help Democra
 ts rebuild trust\, win tough races\, and flip the House. We're bringing peo
 ple together to build the community of real people\, having real conversati
 ons with real people. During Ground Truth phone banks\, we will talk to as 
 many people as possible and focus on listening. \n\nAt this phone bank\, we
 ’ll:\n\n- Call ALL types of voters -- not just those who vote like us.\n\n-
  Have real conversations that LISTEN deeply to voters’ concerns.\n\n- Gathe
 r insights to share with campaigns\, so they can be responsive to voters’ n
 eeds and smarter with their messaging\, targeting\, and outreach.\n\nDon’t 
 worry if it’s your first time—training\, materials\, and support are all pr
 ovided. Just come prepared with your phone and laptop or computer!\n\nWe re
 commend using earbuds or using speakerphone to free up your hands as well! 
 \n\n––\n\nAbout the program:\n\nThis isn’t traditional phone banking—it’s a
  whole new way of talking to voters. Together\, we’ll gather authentic insi
 ghts from communities\, use cutting-edge tools to capture what we hear\, an
 d share it back with campaigns to strengthen their efforts.\n\nWhy we’re st
 arting early: We launched a year ahead of the midterms to build power befor
 e campaigns get off the ground.\n\nHow we’ll go big: Calling every voter\, 
 not just the ones we normally rely on\, so every conversation builds a more
  complete picture of the electorate.\n\nHow we’ll go deep: Practicing empat
 hetic listening and real conversations that uncover voters’ “Ground Truth\,
 ” not just checking boxes on a script.\n\nPaid for by Swing Left\, Swinglef
 t.org\, not authorized by any candidate or candidate’s committee.\n\nHow to
  prepare:\nThanks for signing up to join the Ground Truth phone banking pro
 gram! Together\, we can transform how we talk with voters\, rebuild trust\,
  and swing the most competitive races.\n\nThere will be a training at the b
 eginning of the phone bank\, so don't worry if this is your first time.  \n
 \nPlease be sure to have your laptop/ computer charged and ready to go!\n\n
