DESCRIPTION:Triangle Board Games and Bars\nCome play games at Gamers Geeke
 ry and Tavern every thursday night!\n\nStarting time is 6:30\, but feel fr
 ee to come in anytime and just hang out for the night. Group is very casua
 l and friendly.\n\nHow it works:\nCome on in\, grab a name tag and pay the
  $2.50 meetup participant fee at the bar area\, find the tables that are r
 eserved for the Meetup group\, play games with others who show up. Food an
 d drinks are available at the bar.\n\nPlease RSVP by noon day of. If less 
 than four people are able to attend a given Wednesday the event will be ca
 nceled.
