SUMMARY:Thursday Community Board Game night at Moondog Meadery
DESCRIPTION:Durham Geeks\nIn conjunction with Moon Dog Meadery\, we contin
 ue to have our Thursday Night Gaming Night from 7 until they kick us out. 
 It's a bit smaller group than the large Monday night extravaganza\, and th
 ere are a lot of drop in and independent groups here as well. Restaurants 
 are open on Thursdays\, so you can Dash you food right inside\, or bring i
 t with you!\n\nMoondog has an extensive and ever-changing collection of ga
 mes that are usually loaned out for a fee\, but on Thursdays (just like on
  Mondays)\, they are all free to play. Usually we can find folks to fill i
 n your table or teach you the basics of the games. I've been hosting it fo
 r a few months now\, and we have had a great time with students returning 
 and bringing in new colleagues\, as well as the faithful ones who attended
  over the summer.\n\nDogs and outside food both allowed and encouraged. Al
 ways free! There is award-winning mead on tap and bottled\, as well as an 
 ever-changing collection of beer\, cider\, THC-infused water\, colas and\,
  yes\, just plain old water to keep you hydrated on your adventure.\n\nAny
  questions? Contact us here at Durham Geeks!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/durham-geeks/events/313454775/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260221T012608Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T012608Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
