DESCRIPTION:<span><p>Please join Democracy Support Group on Hillandale and 
 Engaged Defenders for Democracy every Friday 3-4:00pm (unless it is raining
 ) at Samuels Drive and Hillandale near Croasdaile in Durham.</p><p>Come thr
 ough the welcome entrance at Croasdaile\, 2600 Croasdaile Farm Parkway\, as
 k for directions to Samuels Drive and north parking lot and follow signs fo
 r EVENT PARKING.</p><p>Park anywhere in the north parking lot. We walk out 
 the gate on Samuels Drive.</p><p>Signs are available. Emphasis on policies 
 and not personalities.</p><p>This will be a POSITIVE and nonviolent demonst
 ration. We are here to protect our democracy. We are standing up for what w
 e believe in. We want to inspire people to join us and grow our movement!</
 p><p>Please bring positive signs only. Some examples: Instead of "Stop defu
 nding science" Say "Protect Research" "Immigrants make us stronger" "Housin
 g for all" "Healthcare for all" "Save the planet"</p><p>Make signs about wh
 at you're standing up for -- whether that is the libraries\, DEI\, healthca
 re\, women’s rights</p><p>Please no mocking signs\, no swastikas</p><p>We a
 re excited to see you there and stand together for our country!</p><p>See y
 ou every Friday engaging drivers in Durham.</p><p>Please join our Substack:
 <span> </span><a href="https://substack.com/profile/115484101-engaged-defen
 ders-4-democracy" target="_blank">https://substack.com/profile/115484101-en
 gaged-defenders-4-democracy</a></p><p>For more ED4D Mobilize Events:<span> 
 </span><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/" targe
 t="_blank">https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/</a></p><p><
 a href="https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/event/873284/">
 https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/event/873284/</a> </p><
 /span><u></u><u></u><br><u></u>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260306T223254Z
LOCATION:Samuels Drive and Hillandale\, 2600 Croasdaile Farm Pkwy\, Durham\
 , NC\, 27705
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Freedom Fridays:  Durham at Croasdaile
