DESCRIPTION:<span><p>Please join Engaged Defenders for Democracy every Frid
 ay 4-5:00pm at South Roxboro St. &amp\; Martin Luther King Jr. Parkway\, Du
 rham\, NC 27713.</p><p>This will be a POSITIVE and nonviolent demonstration
 . We are here to protect our democracy. We are standing up for what we beli
 eve in. We want to inspire people to join us and grow our movement!</p><p>P
 lease bring positive signs only. Some examples: Instead of "Stop defunding 
 science" Say "Protect Research" "Immigrants make us stronger" "Housing for 
 all" "Healthcare for all" "Save the planet"</p><p>Make signs about what you
 're standing up for -- whether that is the libraries\, DEI\, healthcare\, w
 omen’s rights</p><p>Please no mocking signs\, no swastikas</p><p>We are exc
 ited to see you there and stand together for our country!</p><p>See you eve
 ry Friday engaging drivers in Durham.</p><p>Please join our Substack:<span>
  </span><a href="https://substack.com/profile/115484101-engaged-defenders-4
 -democracy">https://substack.com/profile/115484101-engaged-defenders-4-demo
 cracy</a></p><p>For more ED4D Mobilize Events:<span> </span><a href="https:
 //www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/">https://www.mobilize.us/eng
 agedefendersfordemocracy/</a></p><p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/engage
 defendersfordemocracy/event/841321/">https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefender
 sfordemocracy/event/841321/</a> </p></span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260306T223305Z
LOCATION:South Roxboro St. & Martin Luther King Jr. Parkway\, Durham\, NC\,
  27713
