DESCRIPTION:Join WolfTrails\, NC State Transportation and the NC State Univ
 ersity Police Department for a hands-on safe cycling workshop designed to h
 elp you ride a bike with confidence and awareness. Participants will naviga
 te an obstacle course\, learn proper hand-signaling techniques and gain exp
 erience shifting gears efficiently for different terrains. We’ll also cover
  key North Carolina bike laws to ensure you understand your rights and resp
 onsibilities on the road.\n\nWhether you’re new to biking or looking to ref
 resh your skills\, this interactive session will build practical knowledge 
 you can immediately apply when biking. Space is limited to 20 participants\
 , so be sure to reserve your spot soon. The workshop will be rescheduled or
  canceled if there is not enough participants.
