DESCRIPTION:In celebration of America 250\, Lincoln County Public Library i
 s hosting an evening with author David Fleming! This event is free and Davi
 d will be discussing his book\, "Who's Your Founding Father"\, which invest
 igates the controversial theory that the Mecklenburg Declaration of Indepen
 dence (MecDec)\, a secret 1775 North Carolina document\, predated and inspi
 red the Declaration of Independence\, suggesting Thomas Jefferson may have 
 plagiarized it and covered it up!
