SUMMARY:St Paddy’s  @ Zinchouse Winery
DESCRIPTION:Discover Durham Together\nMarch in Durham just hits different 
 — a little sunshine\, a little breeze\, and that first real hint that sp
 ring is on the way. Let’s get out of the house and head over to Zinchous
 e for a daytime hang filled with drinks\, fresh air\, and good company.\n\
 nThey’re celebrating St. Paddy’s with bagpipes\, Irish dancers\, and f
 estive vibes all afternoon — so expect a little extra energy (and maybe 
 a little green 🍀).\n\nWe’ve done plenty of activity-based meetups\, s
 o this time we’re keeping it easy: show up\, grab a drink\, mingle\, and
  enjoy the atmosphere at one of the cutest venues around.\n\nFood trucks w
 ill be there if you’re hungry!\n\nHope to see you there!
