DESCRIPTION:Calling all girl scouts to test their shelter building skills! 
 In honor of Girl Scout Birthday Weekend\, Lake Norman will be hosting a she
 lter building activity. Learn about different types of shelters\, what you 
 need to make a good shelter\, and have a chance to test out your own skills
 . This program is limited to 25 scouts\, registration will be through the G
 irl Scouts Website.
