 ion: In this session\, participants will get a deep dive on key trends and 
 interests in NC tax policy over the last decade plus. We will review in gre
 ater detail where North Carolina is with regards to tax decisions\, who has
  a stake in the outcomes from tax decisions and who is engaged in shaping t
 ax policy in North Carolina.  We will consider the discussions of local rev
 enue options\, specifically property tax\, and the current tax proposals fr
