SUMMARY:Cary Jaycees Monthly General Membership Meeting 
DESCRIPTION:Triangle Board Games and Bars\nThe are Cary Jaycees\, your loc
 al crew of young professionals who know how to blend community service wit
 h a whole lot of fun. If you’ve ever wanted to meet awesome people\, mak
 e a real impact\, or build your leadership skills while doing some serious
 ly cool projects\, this is your group. Some of our regular attendees don
 ’t RSVP so please don’t be discouraged if others haven’t RSVPd\n\nTh
 e Jaycees are always looking for new members\, so if you’ve been thinkin
 g about getting more involved in Cary and beyond\, consider this your sign
 . The Jaycees are an 18-40 year old group but we welcome everyone to be an
  alumni member (poorly named as you don't need to be a past member.) We me
 et on the third Tuesday of every month at Gamers Geekery and Tavern at 6:3
 0 PM and would love for you to stop by\, say hello\, and see what they’r
 e all about. We cover the game fee for anyone playing with us and will als
 o have appetizers to share.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/triangle-board-games-and-bars/events/
 313287248/
