DESCRIPTION:Come and learn about the different types of songbirds that call
  Elk Knob home. We will briefly go over how to identify the different types
  of songbirds\, as well as learn their calls\, and learn how to help them t
 hrive in our communities. We will be making DIY bird feeders from natural m
 aterials to wrap up the program! This program is open to all ages\, and all
  materials will be provided. Meet at the Park Office. This is not a peanut 
 allergy friendly event.
