DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260318T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260318T130000
SUMMARY:Lunch & Learn: Building Agents with Granite Workshop
DESCRIPTION:All Things AI (Live)\nIn this workshop\, we will explore writi
 ng AI agents using IBM Granite AI models. We will touch on what are AI age
 nts and explore some different designs for agent development. These design
 s are informed by the experiences of IBMers in developing agents.\nOur fir
 st agent will be a basic Function Calling Agent where will be build the ag
 ent from scratch to learn how agents work. We will then explore other agen
 t designs such as Plan-and-Solve\, Route-and-Solve\, ToolRAG\, and ReAct.\
 nThe workshop agents will use LangGraph with LangChain in their implementa
 tions and use IBM Granite as the language model.\n\n**This event is conduc
 ted in partnership with IBM\, [All Things Open](https://allthingsopen.org)
 \, and [The AIE Network](https://theaie.net).**
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/all-things-ai-live/events/313538303/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260226T114745Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260226T114745Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
