DESCRIPTION:NC Democrats\n \nIt's time to find all the warriors for justice
 !\n\nBuilding power starts with engaging our neighbors. Join fierce female 
 activists from across the land\, Young Democrats\, and friendly neighbors o
 n Wednesday evenings from 6-8pm at NCDP Headquarters in Raleigh or on Zoom 
 (link sent in confirmation email after you sign up) to call friendly Democr
 ats to talk about making a plan to vote in the 2026 midterm elections and i
 nvite them to upcoming events.\n\nThank you for stepping up! No experience 
 necessary. You’ll get all the training you need when we meet. If you join u
 s in-person\, we have snacks and refreshing beverages. Join us to create a 
 closer community and a bluer North Carolina!\n\nHow to prepare:\nHi Friend\
 ,\n\nThank you for signing up for our phone bank! For the best experience\,
  we recommend bringing a  laptop\, desktop\, or a tablet device to our phon
 e bank. A cell phone is not recommended for a user-friendly experience but 
 can be used if necessary. \n\nHere is the Zoom link: \nhttps://us02web.zoom
 .us/j/84409850441\n\nStart preparing now for the phone bank by viewing this
  [helpful YouTube video](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BU6CPwwWTV4).\n\nP
 roblems with setting up your ActionID? Here's a [tip sheet](https://docs.go
 ogle.com/document/d/1PGnpjTn1A0KCm15aNUgKGSkON6BXrEE6UGfmienr-1A/edit?usp=s
 haring).\n\nWe look forward to meeting you!\n\nSee you soon\, \nNC Dems Org
 anizing Team\n\nhttps://www.mobilize.us/ncdems/event/760795/
LAST-MODIFIED:20260226T223819Z
LOCATION:NCDP Headquarters\, 220 Hillsborough St\, Raleigh\, NC\, 27603
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Hybrid Women Working Wednesday Phone Bank
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Durham Resistance": "https://durhamresistance.com/calendar"}
X-SOURCE-ID:durham_resistance_4
