DESCRIPTION:Link to join: https://www.mobilize.us/join/48337815/1:4508c8423
 7dd1c777c77ed635a609586d7d18b4e2c70a6542af94c903ff93716/\n\nHow to join:\nJ
 oin Zoom Meeting\n\n\nhttps://blackvotersmatterfund-org.zoom.us/j/896006706
 61?pwd=B90IL6Wy13HenaML00S2RCMajanZ5M.1\n\n\n\n\n\nMeeting ID: 896 0067 066
 1\n\n\nPasscode: 342549\n\n\n\n\n\n---\n\n\n\n\n\nOne tap mobile\n\n\n+1929
 4362866\,\,89600670661#\,\,\,\,*342549# US (New York)\n\n\n+13017158592\,\,
 89600670661#\,\,\,\,*342549# US (Washington DC)\n\n\n\n\n\nJoin instruction
 s\n\n\nhttps://blackvotersmatterfund-org.zoom.us/meetings/89600670661/invit
 ations?signature=izTjgjtFsOca31LQZXAI2FZyR681QgAYXEvxukqs_P8\n\nJoin Black 
 Voters Matter for our Warrant Clinic phonebank.\n\nWhat is a warrant clinic
 ? A warrant clinic is a ONE-DAY community-led grassroots program designed t
 o help people eliminate their warrants due to misdemeanor offenses and traf
 fic violations. It is an entry point to activism and civic engagement.\n\nW
 hat will you do as a volunteer?: Help us reach out to residents and provide
  them with next steps for their warrant(s).\n\nWe provide training via Zoom
 . Which means\, no matter what state you live in\, you can volunteer!\n\nHo
 w to prepare:\nFill out the volunteer agreement here - https://forms.office
 .com/r/TiaHyteJg9\n\nLearn more about the warrant clinic by:\n1. Creating a
  Moodle account here -  https://learn.blackvotersmatterfund.org/ \n2. Once 
 you account is approved\, look for the warrant clinic training course.\n3. 
 Complete the training course and join us at the next phonebank.\n\nhttps://
 www.mobilize.us/blackvotersmatter/event/888301/
