 tendees will learn practical templates for research\, planning\, communicat
 ion\, and routine tasks\, and apply them in a guided exercise to create a p
 ersonalized Daily Thinking Workflow they can reuse right away.\n\n \n\nWe e
 ncourage you to invite your entire team! This workshop\, hosted by Innovate
  Carolina as part of a series\, is designed to build practical skills that 
 help teams collaborate more effectively\, streamline workflows\, and work s
 marter together. Start your workday at 79° West and invest in tools that ca
 n elevate the way your whole team operates.
