X-SOURCE-URLS:{"NC State University": "https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/smarter-nc-webinar-5552"}
X-SOURCE-ID:ncsu
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Training
DESCRIPTION:Join NC State Industry Extension Services for a webinar that wi
 ll focus on smart manufacturing and the opportunities available through a f
 ederally funded grant for small and medium-sized manufacturers in North Car
 olina who are ready to adopt technology. The webinar's goal is to provide t
 argeted technical assistance to small- to medium-sized manufacturers to inc
 rease awareness of\, access to and implementation of innovative smart manuf
 acturing technologies. The benefits of smart manufacturing are:\n\nImproved
  efficiency: Smart factories can monitor equipment performance and automate
  complex processes\, improving accuracy and reducing human error.Increased 
 productivity: Smart factories can use data to identify issues\, such as whe
 n a machine slows down production and then use artificial intelligence syst
 ems to resolve the issues.Long-term cost savings: Smart factories can use p
 redictive maintenance to identify potential problems early and address them
  at a convenient time\, which can save money.Greater flexibility: Smart fac
 tories can scale production quickly to meet changing demand and can customi
 ze products to meet specific customer needs.You can complete a short applic
 ation to find out if your company is ready to participate in the program. F
 or more information about the webinar\, visit the NC State Industry Extensi
 on Services' website.
DTEND:20260319T150000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022450Z
DTSTART:20260319T140000Z
