DESCRIPTION:Link to join: https://www.mobilize.us/join/48337672/1:f32b1230e
 4d1e4bba7152d92a4fd630ecfb07dfeb49002fae284a6381dac469b/\n\n🧬 Power Half H
 our: Lunchtime Action-Stop the Takeover of Public Schools! \n\nJoin fellow 
 concerned parents and community members live for Thursday Lunchtime Zoom Po
 wer Half Hours for 30 minutes of advocacy. \n\nYou’ll be provided a brief t
 raining\, talking points and a call script and phone numbers for key legisl
 ators.\n\nMake your calls in real time with other advocates to help stop th
 e spread of the corporate takeover of our schools.\n\n·      Under the new 
 SBOE Co-Location Rules (Rule 6A-1.0998271)\, the so-called Schools of Hope 
 law is mutating into a full-blown corporate takeover mechanism of our neigh
 borhood schools. These corporations are already targeting neighborhood publ
 ic schools\, seizing public school buildings rent-free. (link to learn more
  somewhere in here)\n\n·      This rule further weakens our neighborhood sc
 hools\, stripping control from parents and school boards\, and draining muc
 h needed funding and resources our children need.\n \n📞 Join fellow advoca
 tes live on Zoom\n🗣️ Get a call script and talking points to contact key l
 egislators\n📱 Make your calls together in real time — and help stop the sp
 read!\nYour voice is part of the cure. Together\, we can protect our school
 s from corporate takeover and restore local control.\nZoom in. Speak out. S
 top the spread.\n\nhttps://www.mobilize.us/strongflschools/event/862913/
LAST-MODIFIED:20260204T152833Z
LOCATION:Virtual event
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:🧬 Power Half Hour: Lunchtime Action to Stop the Takeover of Public
  Schools
