DESCRIPTION:Presenter: Duke Arts Presents\n\nMarc Ribot performs re-interp
 retations and re-framings of Bob Dylan’s mid 1960s-era visionary poetry\
 , the poetic environment from which Dylan’s work emerged\, and the visio
 nary poetry/music that emerged from it.
