DESCRIPTION:The New Bern Historical Society invites you to an exciting stor
 ytelling event\, the Hallowed Ground Lantern Tour\, March 19-21\, 2026\, 6-
 9pm. New Bern Battlefield Park\, site of the first Battle of New Bern\, is 
 host to this intriguing event. The tour takes you on a guided\, lantern-lit
  walk through the wooded battlefield trails\, where spirits of real charact
 ers from New Bern's past will share their very human and inspiring stories 
 of courage and conviction.
