SUMMARY:Triangle Tech Net
DESCRIPTION:Triangle TechBreakfast\n**Triangle Tech Net: Your Next Big Mov
 e Starts Here.**\n\nThe Triangle’s fastest-growing tech networking event
  is back — and we’re turning up the energy.\n\nWhether you're eyeing y
 our next career move or searching for top-tier talent\, *this* is where th
 e Triangle's tech ecosystem comes to connect\, collaborate\, and create re
 al opportunities.\n\nMarch 20th\, 2026\n7:30–9:30 AM\n**No entry will be
  permitted after 8:15 AM**\n6501 Weston Parkway\, Suite #300\, Cary\, NC 2
 7513\nBusiness Casual\n\n**What's In It For You:**\n**Direct Access to Dec
 ision Makers** — Meet hiring managers\, recruiters\, tech leaders\, and 
 peers face-to-face.\n**Actionable Insights** — Learn what’s working *r
 ight now* in hiring\, career moves\, and talent acquisition.\n**Off-Market
  Opportunities** — Discover jobs\, partnerships\, and connections you wo
 n’t find posted online.\n**Real Community** — Build a network that act
 ually works for you.\n**This isn’t a coffee-and-business-card swap. It
 ’s your chance to move the needle.**\n\nAdmission is free — but space 
 fills fast. Reserve your spot today.
