DESCRIPTION:In honor of NC Arbor Day\, join a ranger at Boone Fork Parking 
 Area (milepost 299.9 on the Blue Ridge Parkway) for a tree ID hike along th
 e Upper Boone Fork Trail. Learn how to ID some common tree and shrub specie
 s of the high country based on leaves\, buds\, and bark.\n\nThis 1.5 mile e
 asy hike does have some tree roots and rocks to walk over\, so please wear 
 appropriate hiking shoes and dress for the weather.\n\nThere are no bathroo
 ms at Boone Fork Parking Area.
