DTSTART:20260321T160000Z
DTEND:20260321T200000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022527Z
UID:1djalhqj3doan4tuc06eesntn1@google.com
CREATED:20260202T152728Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Join the Eno River Association for a day of hands-on\, natur
 e-based discovery as we celebrate<span> <a href="https://www.orangecountync
 .gov/3491/Creek-Week" target="_blank">Orange County Creek Week</a>! </span>
 Splash through one of the Eno’s tributaries with us as we catch and identif
 y macroinvertebrates and other fascinating creek critters. Additional activ
 ities will include short hikes\, arts and crafts\, and insect investigation
 s. Come ready to explore\, learn\, and get a little muddy as we celebrate o
 ur local waterways! </p><p><b>This event is FREE and registration is NOT re
 quired.</b> Drop by anytime between noon and 4pm. <b>All ages welcome. </b>
 </p><p><em>Restrooms are available on-site. Two accessible parking spaces c
 onnect the paved sidewalk to the pavilion. At least one activity will take 
 place in the paved pavilion. </em></p><p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:e
 ducatio@enoriver.org" target="_blank">education@enoriver.org</a> <wbr />for
  more information about this event.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260210T154001Z
LOCATION:Confluence Natural Area\, Hillsborough\, NC 27278
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:ERA - Creek Week at the Confluence Nature Fun Day
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
