X-SOURCE-ID:durham_resistance_2
X-SOURCE:Durham Resistance
URL:https://durhamresistance.com/calendar
DTSTART:20260321T183000Z
DTEND:20260321T200000Z
RRULE:FREQ=MONTHLY;BYDAY=3SA
DTSTAMP:20260307T022544Z
UID:r82vcv6r7msrt1u3ni88m8beko@google.com
CREATED:20260108T022208Z
DESCRIPTION:Come join Engaged Defenders for Democracy as we partner with th
 e Overpass Coalition to have a Unified Bridge Brigade that covers bridges i
 n the Triangle and beyond on the third Saturday of the month. We will have 
 protectors on multiple bridges to show that we are not going away\, we are 
 not backing down\, and we support our neighbors and workers. We also are un
 iting all of us over billionaires.\n\nWe will have message about peace\, un
 ity\, and defending our Constitution.\n\nWe will host a Visibility Brigade 
 event where drivers see our protectors and signs as they drive under overpa
 sses in Durham\, Raleigh\, Cary\, Pittsboro\, and Chapel Hill. (we are coor
 dinating with 10 other states).\n\nPlease use the SignUp Genius to sign up 
 for the bridge you will attend: \n\n<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=h
 ttps://www.signupgenius.com/go/10C0549A5AA23A1F8C43-61318184-cultivating%23
 /&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw37HWRXd8toiUx9B8
 XiYVXn" target="_blank">https://www.signupgenius.com/go/10C0549A5AA23A1F8C4
 3-61318184-cultivating#/</a> \n\nEven in cooler temperatures\, sunburn and 
 dehydration can be a problem. Please bring water\, snacks\, sun screen\, a 
 hat\, sunglasses\, and clothing suitable for the weather. The bridges get v
 ery breezy.\n\nYou can learn details by visiting our website.\n\n<a href="h
 ttps://www.google.com/url?q=https://durhamresistancehub.com/btfsite&amp\;sa
 =D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw0zG_juUMfr4iBTGV5e60UH" t
 arget="_blank">https://durhamresistancehub.com/btfsite</a>\n\nWe will ask p
 eople to bring American flags and smaller signs if they have cars and pedes
 trians on the bridge. Please also bring Rainbow flags\, Mexican flags\, and
  Palestine flags.\n\nPlease tell your friends to come.\n\nPeople loved driv
 ing under bridge after bridge seeing our protectors up there sharing a unif
 ied message. Please be part of this next coordinated event!\n\nPlease join 
 our Substack: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://substack.com/pr
 ofile/115484101-engaged-defenders-4-democracy&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calenda
 r&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw3y7Kv9RwiMPWcPPUFQih9k" target="_blank">https:/
 /substack.com/profile/115484101-engaged-defenders-4-democracy</a>\n\nFor mo
 re ED4D Mobilize Events: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.
 mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp
 \;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw1xqNbFip0P6DfK4plFB1D7" target="_blank">https://www.
 mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/</a>\n\nHave accessibility question
 s? The first link above includes an interactive map of participating bridge
 s with information on locations\, parking\, accessibility and restrooms. Th
 is will help you choose a bridge that is right for you. If you have further
  questions\, reply to your registration email\nto confirm your requirements
  or request more information.\n\n<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http
 s://www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/event/842855/&amp\;sa=D&amp
 \;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw0gzPrDc81JbaMEA1Ju88o3" target=
 "_blank">https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/event/842855/<
 /a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T203212Z
LOCATION:Bridges will vary across the Triangle\, Durham\, NC\, 27705
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Triangle Unified Bridge Brigade: 3rd Saturday of the month
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
