SUMMARY:Sunday Community Game Day at Lakewood Social
DESCRIPTION:Durham Geeks\nWhat is up\, my fellow humans! After a sad depar
 ture from our friends at Bull City Solera (RIP) we have quickly found some
  new stomping grounds! Join us at Lakewood Social for some Sunday afternoo
 n board gaming shenanigans! As always\, we always bring an egregious numbe
 r of games\, so feel free to come in and let us teach you something new! E
 ven if you’re new to board games or just want to try something new\, we 
 will get you a seat and make sure you don’t have to stumble through a ru
 lebook. Of course\, you are more than welcome to bring a game of your own 
 to play if you’re a seasoned gamer (or just really love that ONE game!) 
 we will get it to the table!\n\nLakewood Social offers a great selection o
 f delicious grub and a huge variety of beverages to choose from\, no matte
 r what your taste. They have plenty of table space as well as space to get
  up and move around! It is going to be all around a pretty great time!! No
 t to mention that we have a great group of friends that will make you feel
  right at home! So come on out and let's show Lakewood some of that good D
 urham Game Community LOVE!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/durham-geeks/events/313460632/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260221T120456Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T120456Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
