UID:5t2mu9iq2uap683hbnjm84tugv@google.com
CREATED:20260221T203224Z
DESCRIPTION:Please join Engaged Defenders for Democracy on Sunday\, March 2
 2nd from 1pm-2:30pm as we host “Cultivating Courage on College Cuads” a pea
 ceful visibility event designed to build courage and unity among college st
 udents in support of democracy. \n\nPlease sign up for your corner on SignU
 p Genius:  \n\n<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.signupgeni
 us.com/go/10C0549A5AA23A1F8C43-61997090-copy&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar
 &amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw3wuYV57dpz0ZBvTjzO1yHi" target="_blank">https://
 www.signupgenius.com/go/10C0549A5AA23A1F8C43-61997090-copy</a>\n\nWe are co
 mmemorating the Feb 1st Sit-In at Woolworths in 1960 led by college student
 s at North Carolina A&amp\;T College. We need more college students joining
  our current movement.\n\nThe visibility event has two purposes. The first 
 is to promote engagement among college students to exercise their civic rig
 hts to demonstrate\, contact their elected officials\, and learn more about
  what his happening in this country. Also\, specifically in NC\, we want to
  educate students as voting rights are being curtailed\, specifically by el
 iminating some early voting locations that were on college campuses. \n\nTh
 e second purpose is to encourage students to vote early and register during
  early voting.\n\nPeople need to bring their own signs with messages like\,
  &quot\;Rise up&quot\; &quot\;Join Us!&quot\; &quot\;College students have 
 power!!&quot\; &quot\;Stand up\, you are not alone!” “Resist!” “Courage is 
 contagious!” &quot\;Call your elected officials&quot\; &quot\;Vote&quot\; “
 Dissenting is patriotic!” Please also make signs saying\, “Protect our plan
 et” “Affordability matters” and “Stop Gaza genocide.”\n\nWe ask non-student
 s to bring extra signs in case some of the students do not have them.\n\nPl
 ease spread the word to any college student you know to see if they might o
 rganize this event at their college.\n\nEach participant plays an essential
  role: being visible\, being brave\, and encouraging others to do the same.
  The goal is to create a ripple of courage that spreads across our college 
 campuses and beyond.\n\nPlease join our Substack: <a href="https://www.goog
 le.com/url?q=https://substack.com/profile/115484101-engaged-defenders-4-dem
 ocracy&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw3y7Kv9RwiMP
 WcPPUFQih9k" target="_blank">https://substack.com/profile/115484101-engaged
 -defenders-4-democracy</a>\n\nFor more ED4D Mobilize Events: <a href="https
 ://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy
