X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: Data Science Raleigh": "https://www.meetup.com/data-science-nc/events/313619206/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_data_science_raleigh
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Data Science Raleigh
UID:event_313619206@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260307T022536Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260325T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260325T150000
SUMMARY: Building with Mistral: Open\, Powerful\, and Ready to Scale
DESCRIPTION:Data Science Raleigh\nExplore how to develop and deploy Enterp
 rise AI applications with Mistral AI in this practical\, insight-driven se
 ssion. We’ll walk through Mistral’s full model spectrum—from Large t
 o Small—and how to select the right capabilities for your specific use c
 ase.\n\nYou’ll get an introduction to Mistral AI Studio and learn how to
  begin building\, customizing\, and managing AI applications with speed an
 d control. The session will also cover flexible deployment pathways\, incl
 uding serverless\, cloud\, on-premise\, Cloud-VPC\, and dedicated instance
 s—so you can align infrastructure with enterprise requirements.\n\n**Wha
 t You’ll Learn:**\n\n🔹 **Model Selection Strategy:** Understand the L
 arge-to-Small model spectrum and when to use each.\n🔹 **Application Dev
 elopment:** Build and tailor AI applications in Mistral AI Studio.\n🔹 *
 *Flexible Deployment Options:** Compare serverless\, cloud\, on-prem\, VPC
 \, and dedicated setups.\n🔹 **Production Best Practices:** Apply practi
 cal guidance to move AI projects into enterprise-scale production.\n\nGain
  the clarity and tools needed to take AI initiatives from experimentation 
 to reliable\, production-ready systems.\n\n**[Register here](https://hubs.
 ly/Q045pnzM0)**
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/data-science-nc/events/313619206/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260303T163800Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260303T163800Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
