 he power of design to shape the places we live\, work\, and gather. Step i
 nside an inspiring\, high energy studio space that reflects the bold\, inn
 ovative spirit of Durham itself. Meet the architects\, engineers\, interio
 r designers\, and planners who are elevating the human experience through 
 design\, right here in the Triangle and across the globe. And yes\, come h
 ungry and thirsty\, there will be plenty of food and drinks for everyone a
 s we toast to this exciting new chapter. Why You’ll Want to Be There DLR
  Group is a 100 percent employee owned\, global integrated design firm cel
 ebrating 60 years in 2026. Their work is deeply rooted in sustainability\,
  
