 or Growth allows students to engage in various activities\, such as board g
 ames\, role-playing games and virtual reality to promote emotional wellness
 \, social skills and personal growth. The activities occur in a supportive 
 environment that encourages self-expression through play\, helping students
  build confidence and develop healthy relationships with peers. All student
 s are welcome to participate as often as they desire.
