DESCRIPTION:Outdoor Flow Yogis\nJoin Erica at [Weaver Street Market](https
 ://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/location/raleigh/) for donation-based\, ope
 n level yoga and mat pilates classes from 6:15-7pm on select Thursdays in 
 March. Expand your movement practice and uplift our local community. Self-
 care never felt so good!\n\n2nd Thursday - **45min YOGA FLOW + CHILL** int
 egrates breathwork\, flowing waves of movement\, and a restorative cool do
 wn for a full body flow and wind-down\n\n4th Thursday - **45min PILATES MA
 T FLOW** combines core-focused matwork from Joseph Pilates' original mat s
 equence to strengthen your powerhouse\n\nClasses take place upstairs in th
 e Weaver Street Market event space. Street parking is free after 6pm - bri
 ng your own mat and a water bottle.\n\n**Sliding scale pricing to pay-what
 -u-can via cash\, venmo\, or paypal.** *NOTE - 50% of the proceeds from ea
 ch class will be donated to local organizations providing nutrition assist
 ance to those in need.*
