 ries. Join us for this special lecture presented by Yury Gogotsi\, the Char
 les and Ruth Bach Endowed Chair at Drexel University. His talk is titled “B
 uilding Blocks for Technology of the Future: MXenes and Beyond."\n\nGogotsi
  is a pioneer in nanomaterials and energy storage\, known for developing a 
 new family of carbides and nitrides called MXenes.
