DESCRIPTION:ASA DataFest at NC State\, hosted by the Data Science and AI Ac
 ademy (DSA)\, is an annual undergraduate data analysis competition where te
 ams unveil a surprise\, real-world dataset and present their findings to ju
 dges from industry and academia.\n\nThe event is fast-paced\, collaborative
  and a great way for students from all majors to apply data science skills 
 beyond the classroom while connecting with mentors\, employers and peers ac
 ross North Carolina.\n\nHere is why you should participate:\n● Apply analyt
 ical skills to real datasets from real organizations\n● Build teamwork\, co
 mmunication and data storytelling skills\n● Connect with mentors\, judges a
 nd employers\n● Strengthen your resume or graduate school applications\n● J
 oin a growing data science community across North Carolina
