SUMMARY:Annual Open House | College of Veterinary Medicine
DESCRIPTION:Join us at North Carolina State University’s Annual Open House | College of Veterinary Medicine event! We’re happy to be participants in this event with NCSU for another awesome year! Come meet a handful of our adoptable dogs\, participate in raffle drawings for great prizes\, and visit one of the top veterinary medicine colleges in the United States! With an afternoon schedule full of dog demonstrations\, equine demonstrations\, live presentations\, a teddy bear clinic for the kiddos\, and more — it’s sure to be an incredible day. \n📍 1060 William Moore Drive\, Raleigh\, NC 27607 \n📆 Saturday\, March 28\, 2026 from 9 a.m. to 3 p.m.
URL:https://secondchancenc.org/event/annual-open-house-college-of-veterinary-medicine/
