  No Kings Rally on March 28th. The march will begin at 10:30 AM\, and Marsh
 als are essential to ensuring the event runs safely\, smoothly\, and succes
 sfully.\n\n⚠️ All Marshals must arrive by 10:00 AM (30 minutes early) for t
 raining at the march starting location:\n📍 211 West Parrish Street\n\nMars
 hal responsibilities will vary and may include:\n\n-Walking behind the marc
 h to help it move safely and efficiently\n-Standing at intersections to gui
 de participants along the route\n-Helping ensure marchers reach the rally p
 oint\n-Distributing water to participants\n-Monitoring the crowd for any me
 dical emergencies and alerting leadership as needed\n\nMarshals play a crit
 ical role in keeping our community safe and organized while we raise our vo
 ices together. If you’re ready to step up and help lead from the front (and
  the back!)\, we’d love to have you on the team.\n\nSign up today and help 
 make this rally a success!\n\n<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https:/
 /www.mobilize.us/durhamcountydemocrats/event/907670/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=
