X-SOURCE-ID:durham_resistance_2
X-SOURCE:Durham Resistance
URL:https://durhamresistance.com/calendar
DTSTART:20260328T143000Z
DTEND:20260328T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022544Z
UID:3qss5jb18rusnc64mm90o60q31@google.com
CREATED:20260223T145729Z
DESCRIPTION:Join a coalition of grassroots organizations (Engaged Defenders
  for Democracy\, Democracy Out Loud! Bull City Indivisible\, League of Wome
 n Voters) and unions as we say it loud and say it clear\, No Kings\, No Bil
 lionaires\, and No Business as Usual allowed here!\n\nWe will meet at &quot
 \;The Bull&quot\; (CCB Plaza: 211 W. Parrish Street) at 10:30-1. We will ma
 rch from The Bull to &quot\;The Leaf&quot\; across from the Farmer&#39\;s M
 arket. Bring signs that show that we stand in solidarity with our coalition
  partners as we so no kings in the USA and workers over billionaires. \n\nW
 e have heard many times that people cannot hear the speakers. This time\, w
 e are renting a sound system. We ask for donations to please help pay for t
 his sound system. Please go to the GoFundMe page to donate.\n\n<a href="htt
 ps://www.google.com/url?q=https://gofund.me/c03d3bf6a&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source
 =calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw1hDoeUMD6OP-LnfxEzx6Hu" target="_blank"
 >https://gofund.me/c03d3bf6a</a> \n\nPlease join the Engaged Defenders for 
 Democracy Substack: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://substack.
 com/profile/115484101-engaged-defenders-4-democracy&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=c
 alendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw3y7Kv9RwiMPWcPPUFQih9k" target="_blank">h
 ttps://substack.com/profile/115484101-engaged-defenders-4-democracy</a>\n\n
 For more ED4D Mobilize Events: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https:
 //www.mobilize.us/engageddurhamitesfordemocracy/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=cale
 ndar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw1HNjXvhsaaRZW9d-Z5Bxjt" target="_blank">http
 s://www.mobilize.us/engageddurhamitesfordemocracy/</a>\n\nPARKING:\n\n***Ch
 apel Hill Street Parking Garage 326 E Chapel Hill St\, Durham\, NC 27701\n\
 n***Corcoran Street Parking Garage 110 Corcoran St\, Durham\, NC 27701\n\n*
 **Durham Centre Parking Garage 300 W Morgan St\, Durham\, NC 27701\n\nBATHR
 OOMS:\n\n***We will have port-a-potties available. \n\n***Durham Central Pa
 rk under the pavillion 501 Foster St\, Durham\, NC 27701 (6 min walk)\n\n**
 *Durham County Main Library has bathrooms 300 N Roxboro St\, Durham\, NC 27
 701 (8 min walk)\n\nHANDICAP ACCESS:\n\n***Handicap parking extremely limit
 ed. Consider being dropped off early.\n\n***No stairs. Just regular sidewal
 ks with normal curb ramps.\n\n***Expect large crowds. No seating. Get there
  early to find a place on the plaza to be and bring your own chair if neces
 sary.\n\n\nWhat began in 2025 as a single day of defiance has become a sust
 ained national resistance to tyranny\, spreading from small towns to city c
 enters and across every community determined to defend democracy. Our peace
 ful movement is bigger than ever.\n\nWhen our families are under attack and
  costs are pushing people to the brink\, silence is not an option. We will 
 defend ourselves and our communities against this administration’s unjust a
 nd cruel acts of violence.\n\nOn March 28th\, rise up\, take to the streets
 \, and say it loud: no thrones\, no crowns\, no kings. We’re not watching h
 istory happen—we’re making it. Join us.\n\n*A core principle behind all No 
 Kings events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participan
 ts to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagr
 ee with our values and to act lawfully at these events. Weapons of any kind
 \, including those legally permitted\, should not be brought to events.*\n\
 n<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.mobilize.us/engagedefend
 ersfordemocracy/event/909178/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp
 \;usg=AOvVaw39vuVIJD2iV1SomwCJU1nF" target="_blank">https://www.mobilize.us
 /engagedefendersfordemocracy/event/909178/</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260223T145729Z
LOCATION:211 W Parrish St\, Durham\, NC\, 27701
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:No Kings\, No Billionaires\, No Business as Usual
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
