X-SOURCE-ID:ncsu
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Student Life
DESCRIPTION:The Native American Student Association\, Multicultural Student
  Affairs (MSA) and the American Indian Science and Engineering Society will
  host the 36th Annual Native American Student Association Powwow. Join us f
 or a time of gathering\, family and celebration of Indigenous culture. The 
 Powwow will feature vendors\, traditional drum groups and the display of di
 fferent Indigenous dance styles. The event is a time for not only the Nativ
 e community to come together but also for the NC State community to come le
 arn and engage with this rich culture.\n\nThe Powwow and all MSA-sponsored/
 supported programs and initiatives are open to all students.
DTEND:20260329T090000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022451Z
