X-SOURCE-ID:nc_cultural_resources
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Celebrations & Commemorations
DESCRIPTION:Throughout our four-day eggstravaganza\, event tickets give you
  access to our museum grounds and exhibit buildings and include a visit wit
 h the Easter Bunny! You’ll be able to take your own photos\, or for an addi
 tional charge\, have our professional onsite photographer take your family’
 s photos. Enjoy the springtime weather as you explore the museum exhibits f
 eaturing model train layouts\, trains\, airplanes\, automobiles\, trucks\, 
 and more.\n\n\nUpgrade your visit with a leisurely 25-minute train ride exp
 erience aboard our specially decorated Easter-themed train! While riding th
 e rails through our 60-acre museum site\, you’ll be greeted by the Easter B
 unny who will be passing out treats to the kids. Your ticket also allows yo
 u to visit the museum grounds and exhibit buildings. Before or after your r
 ide\, you’ll be able to enjoy a visit with the Easter Bunny and all the oth
 er activities!
DTEND:20260329T210000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022458Z
DTSTART:20260329T160000Z
GEO:35.687243;-80.433348
LOCATION:North Carolina Transportation Museum
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Easter Bunny Express
