DESCRIPTION:Join Ranger Carson for a peaceful hike around the park’s lake a
 s we slow down and reconnect with nature. Along the way\, we’ll explore sim
 ple mindfulness practices and discuss how they can be intertwined into our 
 everyday routines. At the end of our walk\, we'll go onto the beach for a g
 uided meditation designed to help you feel grounded\, calm\, and refreshed.
  This is an interactive program with limited space. To register\, email car
 son.orton@ncparks.gov.
