DESCRIPTION:Come join the Sustainability Stewards in making personalized su
 ncatchers out of bioplastics. Participants will learn about carbon and blue
  economies and how these cycles influence our lives and careers. After a sh
 ort presentation\, the stewards will guide attendees in making suncatchers 
 out of bioplastics\, complete with dried flowers. This is the fourth event 
 in the Sustainability Stewards Educational Series. Attendees can collect on
 e of five stickers offered for this series.
