X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: Data Science Raleigh": "https://www.meetup.com/data-science-nc/events/312860655/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_data_science_raleigh
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Data Science Raleigh
UID:event_312860655@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260307T022536Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260331T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260331T160000
SUMMARY:Plug & Play: Live AI Workflows in Action
DESCRIPTION:Data Science Raleigh\nForget static demos and slide decks. Plu
 g & Play Sessions are all about showing\, not telling. In this hands-on we
 binar series\, you'll see tech leaders walk through their AI product in re
 al time\, highlighting exactly how it works in the wild: setup\, workflows
 \, integrations\, all in just 30 minutes.\n\nBuilt on the momentum of our 
 AI Demo Day format\, Plug & Play goes deeper. Presenters slow down and dig
  in: demonstrating usability\, showing off speed to value\, and guiding at
 tendees through common real-world scenarios. It’s a rare opportunity to 
 see how tools behave under actual conditions\, not just polished slides.\n
 \nExpect 2–3 hours of back-to-back\, engaging walkthroughs. Attendees ar
 e encouraged to click along live\, ask questions\, and walk away with more
  than awareness—usable knowledge.\n\n**Key Takeaways:**\n\n1️⃣ **Rea
 l Product Experience:** See full workflows in motion—not just the highli
 ghts.\n\n2️⃣ **Usability in Focus:** Evaluate ease of use\, integratio
 n paths\, and how quickly value is delivered.\n\n3️⃣ **Interactive Lea
 rning:** Follow along live and get answers as you go.\n\n4️⃣ **Depth O
 ver Demos:** A deeper understanding of how AI tools actually fit into your
  stack.\n\n**[Register here](https://hubs.ly/Q042c9tg0)**
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/data-science-nc/events/312860655/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260113T093338Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260113T093338Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
