BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"UNC Chapel Hill": "https://calendar.unc.edu/event/laughter-humor-and-play-to-reduce-stress"}
X-SOURCE-ID:unc_chapel_hill
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:Professional comedians shouldn’t be the only people to use smil
 ing\, laughter\, humor and play as part of their daily routine. These skill
 s are valuable for everyone. A good smile has long been a key tool for anyo
 ne who needs to influence others. Laughter is now shown to improve our pain
  tolerance. Humor and play can be the building blocks of problem-solving. T
 ogether they can improve our happiness and effectiveness.\n\n \n\nWorkshop 
 Objectives\nAt the end of this workshop\, you will be able to:\nUnderstand 
 the benefits of smiling for:\n• Improving your mood\n• Keeping a positive f
 ocus through an easy exercise\n• Building confidence and receptiveness amon
 g others\nUse laughter to:\n• Improve cardiovascular health by practicing v
 oluntary laughter\n• Enjoy the social dynamic of group behavior\n• Reduce s
 tress\nUse humor and play to:\n• Have fun by building simple jokes\n• Impro
 ve creativity by keeping editing separate from the creative process\n• Buil
 d relationships by saying\, “Yes\, and…”\n\n \n\nClick on Carolina Talent r
 egistration link and select the “Request” button to automatically enroll.
DTEND:20260402T150000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022131Z
DTSTART:20260402T140000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Laughter\, humor and play to reduce stress
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51269615547837
URL:https://calendar.unc.edu/event/laughter-humor-and-play-to-reduce-stress
END:VEVENT
