X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Community Events
DESCRIPTION:The College of Design Fish Market will host Something Old\, Som
 ething New on April 3 from 6-11 p.m. at the Fish Market Gallery\, 133 Fayet
 teville St. in Raleigh. Explore this year's exhibition lineup.\n\nSomething
  Old\, Something New is a show that focuses on nostalgia and acknowledges h
 ow far you’ve come as an artist. We encourage students to submit art from t
 heir past alongside art they’ve created recently to visually show their pro
 gress. All past artworks will be considered\, from childhood drawings to fr
 eshman studio and beyond.\n\nParking is available at the Municipal Parking 
 Deck\, 201 West Morgan St. in Raleigh.
DTEND:20260404T030000Z
