BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"NC State University": "https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/paddling-at-falls-lake"}
X-SOURCE-ID:ncsu
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Student Life
DESCRIPTION:Come explore the serene waters of the Beaver Dam area of Falls 
 Lake on a guided paddling adventure. This unique reservoir offers a tranqui
 l paddling experience away from motorized boat traffic\, making it ideal fo
 r beginners and wildlife enthusiasts alike. Paddle the lake and explore sma
 ll coves while being surrounded by a forested landscape that serves as a ro
 okery for herons\, ospreys and bald eagles.\n\nPrior paddling experience is
 n't required to participate\, but participants must be able to swim and wil
 l undergo a swim test during a pre-trip meeting. Transportation\, equipment
  and instruction are included in the trip.
DTEND:20260404T160000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022451Z
DTSTART:20260404T120000Z
GEO:36.017703;-78.686073
LOCATION:Falls Lake State Recreation Area
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Paddling at Falls Lake
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51560066804707
URL:https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/paddling-at-falls-lake
END:VEVENT
