 for the tunes\, the food\, the coffee or just to take a moment and enjoy yo
 urself\, we've got you covered.\n\nYou'll discover a new performer every We
 dnesday afternoon with artist coordination by Oak City Music Collective. We
 'll feature a range of fresh sounds from local solo and duet projects from 
 the Triangle and beyond.\n\nFree parking is available at the Oval West Park
 ing Deck. To park there for free\, validate your license plate using our QR
  code upon arrival.
