 in what is expected to be one of the most competitive Senate races of 2026.
  In a conversation moderated by veteran journalist David Crabtree\, North C
 arolina political strategists Jonathan Felts and Morgan Jackson will offer 
 an early preview of the campaign.\n\nJoin us from 5:30-7 p.m. on April 8 in
  the Frank Porter Graham Student Union Auditorium for this event. \n\nStude
 nts who attend in person can earn CLE credit. Join us for pizza in the lobb
 y afterward!
