CATEGORIES:Community Events
DESCRIPTION:As part of the 50th anniversary celebration of the founding of 
 the JC Raulston Arboretum\, UNC Press is publishing a revised and updated e
 dition of Bobby J. Ward's 2009 biography of J.C. Raulston\, Chlorophyll in 
 His Veins. Come celebrate the official book launch with Ward's talk on Raul
 ston's life\, legacy and continuing impact on the horticulture world since 
 the first edition.
DTEND:20260410T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022451Z
DTSTART:20260409T223000Z
