DESCRIPTION:The NC State Accessibility Collaborative (NCStAC) is for facult
 y\, staff and students interested in learning about\, sharing and promoting
  accessibility across our university. NCStAC provides a venue for networkin
 g and community building\, knowledge and information sharing\, cross-depart
 mental coordination and peer-to-peer support and collaboration in all areas
  related to accessibility.\n\nView the agendas for our meetings and browse 
 the NCStAC shared folder. A recording and slides will be added to both fold
 ers after each meeting. Join NCStAC  to be added to our Google group and re
 ceive the Zoom link for our meetings.
