CATEGORIES:Lectures and Talks,Community Events
DESCRIPTION:A green chemistry expert panel will focus on the close interact
 ions between the textiles and pulp and paper industries regarding sustainab
 ility. Professionals from various backgrounds will discuss processes such a
 s how pulp and paper products can be used and then dissolved to extract cel
 lulose to form fibers\, which can then be used to develop fashion products.
  A Q&A session with the panelists will follow.
