 ial group admission rates.\n\nSaturday\, April 18\n\nThe general public is 
 invited to enjoy the fun on Saturday\, April 18\, from 9 a.m. – 4 p.m.\, en
 ding out the day with a parade of tractors at 3 p.m.\n\nFor Group Rates: Co
 ntact Meghan DeLapp at 980-305-6298 or meghan.delapp@dncr.nc.gov.\n\nFor Tr
 actor/Equipment registration: Contact June Hall at 980-305-6274 or june.hal
