BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Eno River Association": "https://www.enoriver.org/events/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:eno_river
X-SOURCE:Eno River Association
URL:https://www.enoriver.org/events/
DTSTART:20260418T140000Z
DTEND:20260418T160000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022527Z
UID:0uteeq7odkmkitbr1nt094jtje@google.com
CREATED:20260301T140037Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><u><u><a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/1984194954522?af
 f=oddtdtcreator" target="_blank">Registration is required</a></u></u> - Tic
 kets drop on March 1st at 8:00am!<br>Price: $4<br>*Ticket prices directly s
 upport the work of the Eno River Association. Thank you for your support!</
 p><p><br></p><p>Forest Therapy (sometimes known as Forest Bathing or Shinri
 n-Yoku) broadly means <strong><strong>taking in the forest atmosphere with 
 all of one's senses</strong></strong>. Not simply a walk in the woods\; it 
 is the conscious and contemplative practice of being immersed in the sights
 \, sounds\, and smells of the forest. During your walk\, Aimee Vandemark wi
 ll guide you through invitations to awaken your senses\, slow down\, be pre
 sent\, and reconnect with the nature and rhythm of your surroundings.</p><p
 ><br></p><p>Meet at the pavilion beside the parking lot. This hike will tak
 e approximately two hours (sometimes less\, sometimes more). Please feel fr
 ee to bring water and snacks. Wear comfortable\, weather-appropriate clothi
 ng and shoes. Well-behaved dogs are welcome as long as they are under your 
 control and on a 6-foot leash. Restrooms are available on-site.</p><p><br><
 /p><p>The address is 4214 Highland Farm Rd\, Hillsborough\, NC 27278.</p><p
 >From Hillsborough take Hwy 86 North away from town 1.6 miles from US70. Tu
 rn left on Coleman Loop 1.1 miles. Turn left on Highland Farm Rd 2.4 miles.
  The Confluence is on the left. There is a large sign and a gravel driveway
 . From northern Orange County take Hwy 86 south after passing Walnut Grove 
 Church Rd take the first right on Kenion Rd 1.7 miles. Turn right on Highla
 nd Farm Rd 0.6 miles. The Confluence is on the left. There is a large sign 
 and a gravel driveway.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260301T140037Z
LOCATION:4214 Highland Farm Rd\, Hillsborough\, NC 27278\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:ERA - Guided Forest Therapy Hike - Confluence Natural Area
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
