X-SOURCE-ID:nc_cultural_resources
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:
DESCRIPTION:Hidden Battleship is for the explorer at heart! Join us for an 
 afternoon on a unique\, behind-the-scenes tour of unrestored areas on the B
 attleship. Organized into small groups\, the participants are led to areas 
 in the bow\, third deck\, and below\, and the superstructure\, including al
 l the way to the very top! This program requires climbing ladders\, crossin
 g high hatches\, and going through tight/confined spaces. The tour is limit
 ed to ages 16 and older.\n\n2026 Dates\n\n► January 24\n► February 28\n► Ma
 rch 28\n► April 18\n► November 14\n\n11 am – 5 pm\; $75 (plus tax) per part
 icipant. This program always sells out\, so get your Hidden Battleship tick
 et now! This program is for ages 16 and older.
DTEND:20260418T210000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022458Z
DTSTART:20260418T150000Z
GEO:34.236158;-77.953643
LOCATION: Battleship North Carolina
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Hidden Battleship Tour
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51225005649192
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/hidden-battleship-tour
