X-SOURCE-URLS:{"NC State University": "https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/the-student-art-sale-7012"}
X-SOURCE-ID:ncsu
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Exhibitions,Student Life
DESCRIPTION:Liven up your space or gift original art by supporting NC State
 's talented student artists at the Student Art Sale.\n\nSince 2015\, Arts N
 C State has hosted its annual art sale event\, showcasing the talent and cr
 eativity of students.  The art sale welcomes submissions from all students\
 , whether they study engineering\, chemistry\, media art design technology 
 or any other field\, making the event one of the nation's premier universit
 y art showcases. Every purchase at the art sale empowers students\, fueling
  their artistic journey. Since its start\, our art sale event has contribut
 ed over $100\,000 to student artists\, making a real impact on their lives 
 and careers.\n\nJoin us in supporting and investing in the next generation 
 of artists whose talents transcend disciplines.\n\nThe art sale will be hel
 d at the Gregg Museum of Art & Design.\n\nThe museum has limited parking. W
 e strongly encourage guests to carpool or walk to the museum. Please view a
 vailable parking options before your visit to the museum. ﻿
DTEND:20260418T200000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022451Z
DTSTART:20260418T170000Z
