 uilford County Time Capsule will be ceremonially sealed at the High Point M
 useum. Join us for this special event featuring live music and a rare oppor
 tunity to view the items before they’re sealed away until America’s 300th a
 nniversary.\n\nThis FREE ceremony is open to the public!
