DESCRIPTION:In 1998\, the neuroscientist Jaak Panksepp published a book cla
 ssifying seven primary affective systems or\, more simply\, emotional devel
 opmental states. Mapping Instincts is our collective exploration of these c
 oncepts at play in our bodies and minds. Directed by Mia Self.
