 ative discipline while leveraging access to state-of-the-art labs and studi
 os. Collections span home textiles\, apparel\, fiber art and more. \n\nThe 
 Emerging Designers Textile Showcase will be held at the Textiles Campus on 
 Centennial Campus.\n\nThe Textile Showcase Opening is on Sunday\, April 19\
 , from 3 to 5 p.m. The event is open to the public and free for all.\n\nThe
