 dees the chance to engage directly with presenters\, explore innovative wor
 k happening across campus and connect with the people advancing sustainabil
 ity before the Celebration’s formal program begins at 9:30 a.m.\n\n \n\nThe
  campus community is invited to display their work and/or attend this event
 . Please RSVP by April 7:\n\nReserve your Sustainability Showcase Spot Here
 RSVP to attend the Celebration Here \n\nSponsored by the NC State Universit
 y Sustainability Council\, the Climate and Sustainability Academy and the U
 niversity Sustainability Office\, this event highlights the depth and impac
