 e and share ideas to strengthen climate and sustainability education at our
  university.\n\nThis is your chance to:\n\nShowcase your courses\, programs
  or curricular resources at a tableMeet peers and share ideas with others t
 eaching or working in climate and sustainabilityDisplay a slide in our rota
 ting slideshow\, including QR codes or links so guests can follow up with y
 ouIf you would like to participate in Edujam\, complete the interest form.\
 n\nThis event will immediately follow the Celebration of Sustainability eve
 nt.
