BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: Durham Writers Group": "https://www.meetup.com/dwg-writers/events/tttfwtyjcgbcc/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_durham_writers
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Durham Writers Group
UID:event_tttfwtyjcgbcc@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260307T022533Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260421T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260421T213000
SUMMARY:*IN-PERSON* SF/F Group
DESCRIPTION:Durham Writers Group\nWe will be at the People's Solidarity Hu
 b at 1809 Chapel Hill Rd\, Durham. This venue does not serve food or drink
 \, but feel free to bring your own. There is a kitchenette for our use\, b
 ut be sure to clean up afterwards. The space might be a little cozy\; plea
 se consider masking or staying home if you have a respiratory ailment.\n\n
 This sub-group focuses on Speculative Fiction\, including Science Fiction\
 , Fantasy and Horror. If you have anything that falls under that category 
 — be it short story\, poem\, novel-in-progress or screenplay — then co
 me! We'd love to hear from you.\n\nOur format allows each reader 15 minute
 s to present their work aloud\, followed by approximately 20 minutes of fe
 edback from the other attendees. To ensure fairness\, each attendee is lim
 ited to 1 minute of Initial Feedback time. During that period\, the author
  remains silent. Next\, we have a 5 minute Free-For-All discussion about t
 he work -- then the author may speak. (We usually get through three reader
 s.)\n\nThough not required\, in order to receive more in-depth feed-back\,
  readers may post their work in advance on our Google Group:\nhttps://grou
 ps.google.com/d/forum/durham-sff-writers-group\n\nWe ask that participants
  keep their comments constructive and respectful\, focusing on what works 
 or doesn't work in the piece.\n\nWe also ask that readers provide a warnin
 g\, both on the Google Group and during the meeting\, if their story featu
 res content that some readers might find upsetting. This includes descript
 ions of violence or sexual content.\n\nReaders are:\n•\n•\n•\n\nBack
 up Readers are:\n•\n•\n•\n\nDeep Backup:\n•\n\n***\n\n***We meet e
 very Tuesday at the same time\, but alternate between In-Person*** ***and 
 on Zoom. Members may attend both formats\, if desired\, but readers will b
 e listed separately under the In-Person or Zoom weeks.***
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/dwg-writers/events/tttfwtyjcgbcc/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260225T021211Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260225T021211Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
