BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"UNC Chapel Hill": "https://calendar.unc.edu/event/human-in-the-loop-thematic-analysis-using-r-to-apply-current-recommendations-for-incorporating-llms-into-qualitative-research"}
X-SOURCE-ID:unc_chapel_hill
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:Do you want to explore current research recommendations in the 
 literature on incorporating LLMs into qualitative/mixed methods data analys
 is\, or are you interested in implementing LLMs into your qualitative/mixed
  methods workflow?  If so\, this short course is designed for you!\n\nIn th
 is course we will examine current recommendations from the literature regar
 ding integrating AI (specifically LLMs) into the process of qualitative cod
 ing.  Acknowledging that a wide range of qualitative approaches exist\, all
  examples and recommendations in this course will be based on the 6 Phase T
 hematic Analysis Framework proposed by Braun & Clarke 2006 to simplify the 
 course scope.\n\nNo perquisites in qualitative methods or coding are requir
 ed for this course – just bring your computer & your curiosity!\n\nIn the c
 ourse we will:\n\nReview the qualitative approach of Thematic Analysis usin
 g the Braun & Clarke FrameworkGet a high-level\, very big picture understan
 ding of LLMs\, what they are & how they generate “natural language”Examine 
 current recommendations in the literature on incorporating LLMs in Thematic
  AnalysisDo hands-on activities in R that implement some of the current rec
 ommendations using the Braun & Clarke Framework. We will compare our result
 s to published results generated by all human coders using the same dataReg
 istration and fee (refundable for students) are required for Zoom link acce
 ss.
DTEND:20260422T180000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022132Z
DTSTART:20260422T140000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:	"Human-in-the-Loop” Thematic Analysis: Using R to Apply Current Re
 commendations for Incorporating LLMs into Qualitative Research
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51967287028945
URL:https://calendar.unc.edu/event/human-in-the-loop-thematic-analysis-usin
 g-r-to-apply-current-recommendations-for-incorporating-llms-into-qualitativ
 e-research
END:VEVENT
