BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"UNC Chapel Hill": "https://calendar.unc.edu/event/balancing-work-and-life-8344"}
X-SOURCE-ID:unc_chapel_hill
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:Using the philosophy that “those who are happy at home perform 
 better on the job\,” this workshop was developed for those who feel burdene
 d with too many responsibilities and without enough time for personal enjoy
 ment. This workshop will help participants explore and define home responsi
 bilities\, identify career requirements and prioritize leisure time. The re
 sulting better balance will help achieve more in one’s career and at home.\
 n\n \n\nWorkshop Objectives\nAt the end of this workshop\, you will be able
  to:\nIdentify the components of a balanced lifestyle\n• Describe the conce
 pt of balance\n• Identify what is out of balance in your life\n• Describe h
 ow notions of balance have changed over time in your life and historically\
 n• Identify the relationship between stress and balance\nIdentify and explo
 re the balance between home responsibilities\, career requirements\nand lei
 sure activities\n• Describe how to create your own balance diagram\n• Ident
 ify the right questions to achieve balance\n• Describe the role of prioriti
 zation\, limit setting and time management to balancing work and life\n• Id
 entify tips and suggestions on how to achieve balance\n• Identify a persona
 lized action plan to achieve balance in your life\n\n \n\nClick on Carolina
  Talent registration link and select the “Request” button to automatically 
 enroll.
DTEND:20260422T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022132Z
DTSTART:20260422T160000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Balancing Work and Life
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51375401984289
URL:https://calendar.unc.edu/event/balancing-work-and-life-8344
END:VEVENT
