DESCRIPTION:Come celebrate Earth Day with the Rangers at Lake James State P
 ark!\n\nJoin us for a meaningful afternoon of service and fun as we work to
 gether to care for our park. In honor of Earth Day\, we’ll be picking up li
 tter around the Paddy’s Creek Swim Beach and nearby picnic areas to help ke
 ep Lake James beautiful for everyone to enjoy.\n\nAfter our cleanup\, stick
  around for a round of “Oh\, Deer\,” an engaging and interactive game that 
 explores wildlife survival.\n\nWe will meet at 3:30 PM in the Paddy’s Creek
  day-use area at the swim beach. All tools and personal protective equipmen
 t (PPE) will be provided. All ages are welcome to join.
