DESCRIPTION:New Hope Bird Alliance is excited to welcome our community to p
 articipate in our New Hope Birdathon! Grab your binoculars\, gather your fr
 iends\, and get ready to bird this April 23-26 to see how many species you 
 can find while raising funds for New Hope Bird Alliance. Our goal is to rai
 se $15\,000 to help expand our organization's capacity and hire our first p
 aid staff\, an Executive Director. This will enable us to amplify our educa
 tional and conservation efforts\, bringing our passion for birds to a broad
 er audience in the Triangle. The situation for birds and wildlife is deteri
 orating at an unsustainable pace\, but together\, we can make a difference.
  Your support will help us achieve our goals and ensure a brighter future f
 or our feathered friends.<br><br>Birds need our help. Birds need new hope. 
 Join the New Hope Birdathon and make your birding count. Learn more and reg
 ister <a target="_blank" href="https://charity.pledgeit.org/newhopebirdatho
 n"><u>here</u></a>.
LAST-MODIFIED:20260306T185814Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:New Hope Birdathon
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
