DESCRIPTION:A celebration of creativity and growth among sophomore fashion 
 design students in the fashion and textile design program at the Wilson Col
 lege of Textiles\, showcasing their first capsule collections. Each collect
 ion is inspired by iconic designers from the past century and reinterpreted
  through decade-specific research\, pattern-making\, and construction techn
 iques. The pop-up museum highlights emerging designers’ work and shows how 
 historical influences are given a fresh\, modern perspective.\n\nThis event
  is free and open to the public! Please RSVP here!
