X-SOURCE-ID:nc_cultural_resources
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Exhibits & Tours,Guided Tours
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Museum of Early Southern Decorative Arts on Frid
 ays at 2 pm throughout April for Early Life in Southern Homes: A Woman’s Wo
