BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"NC Cultural Resources": "https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/statewide-star-party-mission-to-the-moon"}
X-SOURCE-ID:nc_cultural_resources
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:
DESCRIPTION:Join the Hammocks Beach staff as we host the NC SciFest Star Pa
 rty Event:  "Mission to the Moon".  This is an after hours event filled wit
 h a variety of hands-on space-themed activities for all ages. Families can 
 build and test their own Moon landing modules\, launch stomp rockets\, and 
 construct creative Moon bases while learning about engineering and life in 
 space. Visitors can explore the night sky through telescopes\, listen to cu
 ltural sky stories during Storytelling Under the Stars\, and try challenges
  like the Rover Maze\, Lunar Twister\, and Lunar Bean Bag Toss. Additional 
 rotating activities from NC SciFest offer quick STEM experiences throughout
  the event. Together\, these stations blend science\, imagination\, and exp
 loration to inspire curiosity about our universe.
DTEND:20260425T013000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022459Z
DTSTART:20260424T230000Z
GEO:34.670531;-77.143056
LOCATION:Hammocks Beach State Park
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Statewide Star Party:  Mission to the Moon
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51391896954077
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/statewide-star-party-mission-to-the-mo
 on
END:VEVENT
