 rgaze to see wondrous constellations\, far far away galaxies\, and other ce
 lestial bodies. \n\nStar Party activities will take place at the loop parki
 ng lot at the end of the road of the Fews Ford Access of Eno River State Pa
 rk.\n\nOur Star Party will happen rain or shine\; however\, many activities
  are weather dependent.
