DESCRIPTION:Join us for a living history event that will provide a comprehe
 nsive view of maritime history within the region\, provide context for nava
 l stores production along the lower Cape Fear\, and provide interpretations
  of eighteenth century trades that are relevant to maritime history and sai
 ling. It will contextualize the role of the naval stores industry in Brunsw
 ick's development as a major colonial port. This is a free event for all ag
 es.
DTEND:20260425T200000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022459Z
DTSTART:20260425T140000Z
