CATEGORIES:Celebrations & Commemorations,Festivals & Fairs
DESCRIPTION:Washington County 250 will sponsor an event at the Davenport Ho
 mestead\, intersection of Mt. Tabor Rd. and Anold Hill Rd.\,  Creswell\, NC
  27928 on Saturday April 25\, 2026 from 10 AM till 3 PM. The Homestead\, bu
 ilt by Daniel Davenport after his return from his six month enlistment in t
 he 5th NC will be the scene of living histories\, a house tour\, and period
  music.  The DAR and SAR will sponsor a Wreath Laying Ceremony to honor Dan
 iel Davenport at a monument on the grounds.
DTEND:20260425T190000Z
