DESCRIPTION:Join us on a "Mission to the Moon\," with hands-on activities a
 nd night-sky viewing in beautiful Bertie County! We'll meet at Bertie Beach
  on the Chowan River\, which features a large open field with an expansive 
 view of the night sky. Start off with some hands-on activities to learn abo
 ut the Moon while we wait for dark\, and then we will look at the sky throu
 gh telescopes.\n\nSeveral community partners will be participating as well\
 , including members of local astronomy clubs.
DTEND:20260426T020000Z
