DTSTART:20260426T180000Z
DTEND:20260426T200000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022527Z
UID:0j05llp5b873cg4fnk66d70716@google.com
CREATED:20260219T161741Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><u><u><a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/1983546352536?af
 f=oddtdtcreator" target="_blank">Registration is required</a></u></u> - Tic
 kets drop on March 1st at 8:00am!<br>Price: $4<br>*Ticket prices directly s
 upport the work of the Eno River Association. Thank you for your support!</
 p><p><br></p><p>This is a hike on a well maintained trail. With luck and th
 e right flowering time\, you might see a Ladyslipper orchid! This is an eas
 y hike with a few gentle hills and is known for the beauty of the wildflowe
 rs that bloom each spring. Walking sticks are recommended as we will step o
 ff trail.</p><p><br></p><p>This hike will take approximately two hours (som
 etimes less\, sometimes more). Please feel free to bring water and snacks. 
 Wear comfortable\, weather appropriate clothing and shoes. Well-behaved dog
 s are welcome as long as they are under your control and on a 6 foot leash.
 </p><p>Children under the age of 6 do not require a ticket.</p><p>This even
 t is rain or shine. We will contact you if severe weather is expected that 
 would cause us to cancel the hike.</p><p>There is no need to print your tic
 ket - we have you on the list now!</p><p>If your plans change and you are u
 nable to attend the hike\, please contact hillary@enoriver.org to cancel yo
 ur registration so that we may offer your spot(s) to our waitlist.</p><p><b
 r></p><p>Directions: IMPORTANT - There are two Pump Station trailheads alon
 g Rivermont Road. We will meet at the second trailhead on Rivermont when co
 ming from Cole Mill Road. Park along the road at the bridge over Nancy Rhod
 es Creek\, on Rivermont Drive. We will meet next to the bridge. Rivermont r
 uns between Cole Mill and Valley Springs. The address is 4023 Rivermont Roa
 d\, Durham\, NC 27712.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260219T161741Z
LOCATION:4023 Rivermont Rd\, Durham\, NC 27712\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
