DESCRIPTION:Bring your lunch\, some teammates (or opponents) and your colle
 ctive brainpower to 321 Coffee shop twice a month to compete in team trivia
 . Solo participants are also encouraged to compete. Whether you're a casual
  quizzer or a seasoned trivia champ\, this lunchtime series is the perfect 
 way to test your knowledge and connect with co-workers and friends.\n\nNC S
 tate University librarians will serve as hosts of the competition\, and tri
 via master extraordinaire Dave Provost is our question maker.\n\nThe winnin
 g teams will take home a seasonal 3D printed trophy and a free coffee drink
 \, but the real prize might be the friends we make along the way.
