 ost opioid overdose prevention and response training sessions. During the s
 essions\, you will learn about the opioid epidemic\, warning signs of an ov
 erdose and appropriate ways to respond to an overdose. Participants will re
 ceive a free Narcan (Naloxone) kit\, an opioid overdose reversal medication
 . Please register.
