DESCRIPTION:Click the "Register" button to apply to be a Vendor\, Young En
 trepreneur\, or Sponsor! Get ready for an unforgettable day at the 44th An
 nual Meet in the Street Festival on May 2\, 2026\, from 10 am to 4 pm in d
 owntown Wake Forest! This vibrant celebration is the largest event in town
 \, showcasing over 100 artisan booths\, filled with unique handmade treasu
 res\, a mouthwatering array of food trucks in two courts\, and entertainme
 nt spread throughout the event! Families will love the Children's Village\
 , bursting with fun activities for kids of all ages\, and NEW this year\, 
 Engine Alley- home to over 20 unique vehicles! . With free admission\, the
 re's no reason to miss out on this incredible festival!
