 (Financial Times). \n\n \n\nTickets are available starting at $49. Enjoy a 
 variety of season-long discounts\, available exclusively for Carolina Perfo
 rming Arts’ series performances. \n\n \n\n$11 Student Tickets \n\nUNC stude
 nts + ALL K-college students statewide can purchase $11 tickets for every C
 PA season show. \n\n \n\nChoose Your Price Tickets \n\nFive percent of tick
 ets are released 24 hours before each show at pay-what-you-can pricing. \n\
