CREATED:20251222T173349Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260202T200304Z
UID:24282-1777795200-1777809600@secondchancenc.org
SUMMARY:Racing for Rescues
DESCRIPTION:Mark your calendars for Sunday\, May 3\, 2026\, because you won’t want to miss out on the fun at Wake Med Soccer Park in Cary\, NC! Grab your running shoes\, gear up your furry friends\, and get ready for a morning of fun with furry friends at Racing for Rescues!\n\n\n\nHere’s some of what’s in store:\n\n Timed 5K race for humans and their canine companions with fantastic prizes.\n One-mile walking course for a leisurely stroll with your four-legged pals.\n Show off your creativity in our pet and human costume contest!\n Incredible raffle prizes await\, and you can win even if you’re not present.\n Enjoy complimentary snacks and drinks to keep you fueled.\n Discover amazing vendors\, including a “Make Your Own” Dog Treat bar!\n\n\n\nNot local? Don’t worry — Racing for Rescues offers a hybrid option! No matter where you are in the U.S.\, you can participate and support our cause.
URL:https://secondchancenc.org/event/racing-for-rescues/
LOCATION:Wake Med Soccer Park\, 101 Soccer Park Drive\, Cary\, NC\, 27511\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://secondchancenc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Web_Header_RfR.png
END:VEVENT
