UID:3flgdopipaqihus5e750oud5cs@google.com
CREATED:20260123T172950Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us on the first Sunday of the month as we do a coordinated
  demonstration on multiple corners (Feb 1 is just for colleges and has its 
 own link). All events are from 1pm-2:30pm as we host “Cultivating Courage b
 y Covering Corners\,” a peaceful visibility event designed to build courage
  and unity in support of democracy. \n\nPlease sign up for your corner on S
 ignUp Genius:  \n\nSmall groups will gather on consecutive corners along a 
 key stretch of road\, holding positive\, pro-democracy signs. We will cover
  corners in areas where ED4D does typically do not demonstrate: Creedmoor\,
  Holly Springs\, and XXX. All of these areas are purple. \n\nThe purpose is
  to build motivation for folks to join us. By standing together on multiple
  corners simultaneously\, we show our community that courage is contagious—
 that even small acts of presence can inspire others to stand up for shared 
 values.\n\nEach participant plays an essential role: being visible\, being 
 brave\, and encouraging others to do the same. The goal is to create a ripp
 le of courage that spreads across our community and beyond.\n\nWe will have
  one common sign at each corner. People will need to bring their own signs.
  Please also consider bring an American flag along with one of several othe
 r flags (rainbow flag\, Palestine flag\, Mexican flag\, Ukraine flag)\, to 
 make it clear we are not MAGA. We have rainbow flags for each corner. \n\nP
 lease make signs that say\, “Stand up\, you are not alone!” “Resist!” “Cour
 age is contagious!” &quot\;Call your elected officials&quot\; &quot\;Vote&q
 uot\; &quot\;We the People Have Power!&quot\; &quot\;Start your own demonst
 ration!!&quot\;\n\nPlease join ED4D&#39\;s Substack: <a href="https://www.g
 oogle.com/url?q=https://substack.com/profile/115484101-engaged-durhamites-4
 -democracy&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw3MkrdMQ
 VANb4wodoztKfro" target="_blank">https://substack.com/profile/115484101-eng
 aged-durhamites-4-democracy</a>\n\nFor more ED4D Mobilize Events: <a href="
 https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.mobilize.us/engageddurhamitesforde
 mocracy/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw1HNjXvhsa
 aRZW9d-Z5Bxjt" target="_blank">https://www.mobilize.us/engageddurhamitesfor
 democracy/</a>\n\n<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.mobiliz
 e.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/event/867070/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calend
 ar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw0WpHPJqn2tXvfeX1374LWb" target="_blank">https:
 //www.mobilize.us/engagedefendersfordemocracy/event/867070/</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260123T172950Z
LOCATION:Corners all over the Triangle and beyond!\, Durham\, NC\, 27705
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Cultivating Courage by Covering the Corners
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
