BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"UNC Chapel Hill": "https://calendar.unc.edu/event/mental-health-awareness-for-leaders-7643"}
X-SOURCE-ID:unc_chapel_hill
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:Managing individuals who may be struggling with stress\, anxiet
 y\, depression and other mental health concerns can be a difficult balancin
 g act. Your role is to manage performance and to bring out the best in your
  workforce\, but accomplishing this often requires you to express concern a
 nd support when employees struggle emotionally. Managers often feel uncomfo
 rtable in this aspect of their role and may lack the important skills of “e
 motional management.” This course covers ways employees may present their d
 istress and offers insights and strategies on forging supportive empathic a
 lliances within the role of manager. The session also identifies common mis
 takes managers make in responding to employees in distress and explains com
 munication skills that express support and convey positive expectancy. Part
 icipants are also given information on how to refer employees to the Employ
 ee Assistance Program.\n\n \n\nWorkshop Objectives\nBy the end of this work
 shop\, you will:\n• Understand the universality of mental health issues in 
 the workplace\n• Recognize the most common symptoms of mental illness\n• Id
 entify the most common unhelpful reactions to symptoms\, why they occur and
  how to avoid them\n• Identify ways of expressing compassion and developing
  an alliance with distressed employees\n• Reduce the stigma associated ment
 al illness and promote ways of supporting one another in the workplace\n• R
 ecognize the warning signs of suicide\n• Identify support services and reso
 urces for all leaders and employees\n\n \n\nClick on Carolina Talent regist
 ration link and select the “Request” button to automatically enroll.
DTEND:20260506T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022132Z
DTSTART:20260506T160000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Mental Health Awareness for Leaders
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51375462958731
URL:https://calendar.unc.edu/event/mental-health-awareness-for-leaders-7643
END:VEVENT
