DESCRIPTION:Link to join: https://www.mobilize.us/join/46980077/1:f7b649d24
 e43e5a48ebabb853e7de6c381fb03d181e2d1213b0c0fd06ea5051a/\n\nHow to join:\nP
 lease join our virtual welcome session with this link\n\nAre you a young pe
 rson between 13 and 25 years old who is interested in taking action around 
 preventing gun violence? Join us for our Team ENOUGH welcome session to lea
 rn more about the different ways you can engage. \n\nTeam ENOUGH is a youth
 -led program whose mission is to educate young voices about gun violence an
 d mobilize them to take meaningful action against it. Supported by Brady Un
 ited\, we harness the expertise and experience of today’s youth to advance 
 our intersectional work across the country. \n\nLed by an Executive Council
 \, comprised of students just like us\, we believe that diversity is a stre
 ngth\, and that only when everyone has a seat at the table can we build an 
 effective movement to prevent all gun violence in all communities.\n\nFor u
 s\, preventing gun violence not only requires regulating access to firearms
  but also addressing how systemic racism and environmental factors cause th
 is form of bloodshed to run especially rampant in communities of color. You
  cannot talk about gun violence without talking about police brutality\, wh
 ite supremacy\, the broken criminal justice system\, poverty\, homophobia\,
  access to affordable housing\, or the often barriers separating disadvanta
 ged populations from physical and mental healthcare. \n\nSo if you share th
 is belief\, join us for our Team ENOUGH welcome session and become part of 
 the movement to end gun violence in our lifetime.\n\nHow to prepare:\nWe ar
 e excited to see you soon!\n\nP.S. This is a call for young people from 13-
 25 years old who are interested in getting engaged with the Team ENOUGH pro
 gram. If you are over the age of 25 please sign up for the Brady Welcome Se
 ssion at https://www.mobilize.us/brady/event/274016/\n\nEvent Zoom Link: ht
 tps://us06web.zoom.us/j/84862510973\n\nhttps://www.mobilize.us/brady/event/
 425528/
LAST-MODIFIED:20260101T201412Z
LOCATION:Virtual event
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Team ENOUGH Welcome Session (For Young People Under 26)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
