SUMMARY:*VIRTUAL* SF/F Group
DESCRIPTION:Durham Writers Group\n**Zoom Info Below Description**\n\nThis 
 sub-group focuses on Science Fiction and Fantasy\, so if you have anything
  that falls under that category — be it short story\, poem\, novel-in-pr
 ogress or screenplay — then come! We'd love to hear from you.\n\nOur for
 mat allows each reader 15 minutes to present their work... followed by app
 roximately 20 minutes of feedback from the other attendees. To ensure a fa
 ir opportunity to respond\, each attendee is limited to 1 minute of feedba
 ck time. (We usually get through three readers.)\n\nIf a reader elects to 
 post their work in advance (NOT a requirement!)\, members will be able to 
 access that work at our Google Group:\nhttps://groups.google.com/d/forum/d
 urham-sff-writers-group\n\nWe ask all members to provide a warning\, both 
 on the Google Group and during the meeting\, if their story features conte
 nt that some readers might find upsetting. This includes descriptions of s
 exual violence.\n\nReaders are:\n•\n•\n•\n\nBackup Readers are:\n•
 \n•\n•\n\nDeep Backup:\n\n***\n\n***We meet every Tuesday at the same 
 time\, but alternate between meeting In-Person and on Zoom. Members may at
 tend both formats\, if desired\, but readers will be listed separately und
 er the In-Person or Zoom weeks.***\n\n> Enabled for both audio and video. 
 Users can choose what to share.\n> Users can share their screen/applicatio
 n\, which could be good for reading along.\n> There is a shareable whitebo
 ard.\n> Users can annotate the screen.\n> You can set up polls (host only?
 ).\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting\nhttps://duke.zoom.us/j/640491577\n\nMeeting ID: 6
 40 491 577\nPasscode: 004234\n\nDial by your location\n+1 646 876 9923 US 
 (New York)\n+1 253 215 8782 US\n+1 301 715 8592 US\n\nJoin by SIP\n6404915
 77@zoomcrc.com\n\nJoin by H.323\n162.255.36.11 (US East)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/dwg-writers/events/312995722/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
