BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"NC State University": "https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/building-resilient-supply-chains-the-power-of-domestic-sourcing-webinar"}
X-SOURCE-ID:ncsu
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Training
DESCRIPTION:Are you struggling to find reliable domestic suppliers? If so\,
  attend a webinar hosted by NC State Industry Expansion Solutions to learn 
 a better way. Finding the right supplier is crucial for reducing risk\, ens
 uring product quality and building a resilient business\, especially in the
  face of fluctuating global trade policies. This webinar will introduce a p
 owerful tool: the North Carolina Manufacturing Extension Partnership’s supp
 lier program. Attendees will learn how to connect with vetted domestic supp
 liers who can help them streamline their operations\, drive growth and buil
 d a more resilient supply chain. Discover the types of opportunities availa
 ble and how to access our supplier sourcing and matching services. You shou
 ld attend the webinar if you are a manufacturer with:\n\nExtended lead time
 s and increased frustration with your current supply chainExcess capacity a
 nd is seeking new business opportunitiesVisit the Industry Expansion Soluti
 ons website for more information.
DTEND:20260514T150000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022452Z
DTSTART:20260514T140000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Building Resilient Supply Chains
