  of crafts and games.\n\nThis FREE\, family-friendly event is open to the p
 ublic. No registration is required. The event will take place indoors in th
 e Chatham Community Library's Holmes Family Meeting Room. The Chatham Commu
 nity Library is ADA-compliant\, including wheelchair-accessible parking\, e
 ntrances\, seating\, common spaces\, walkways\, and restrooms. The Holmes F
 amily Meeting Room has an automatic door opener. Free parking is available 
 outside the library. Pets are not allowed - please leave your furry friends
  at home.\n\nThis event is part of our Chatham Celebrates America 250 initi
 ative. See more America 250 events.
