X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Sarah P. Duke Gardens": "https://gardens.duke.edu/event/create-your-own-herbal-cooling-face-mist/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:duke_gardens
X-SOURCE:Sarah P. Duke Gardens
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260517T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260517T160000
DTSTAMP:20260306T212505
CREATED:20251208T230626Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251208T230626Z
UID:14707-1779026400-1779033600@gardens.duke.edu
SUMMARY:Create Your Own Herbal Cooling Face Mist
DESCRIPTION:Develop your relationship with some well-known plants by creating an herbal face mist with Sufia Ikbal-Doucet (they/them)\, herbalist & sovereignty doula. In this hands-on workshop\, we’ll uncover the refreshing power of plants like rose\, aloe\, chamomile and mint. Learn about their healing properties\, tap into deep presence and intuition to deepen your relationship and create a personalized blend to refresh your skin and spirit. All materials will be provided for each participant to create an herbal face mist to take home. \nFee: $42; 20% discount for Duke Gardens members with discount code. \nParking: Fees apply. \nLocation: Onsite at Duke Gardens. Meeting location will be included in a program reminder email sent the week before the program.\n \nAccessibility: This program will take place seated indoors\, in a location accessible by fully paved paths.
URL:https://gardens.duke.edu/event/create-your-own-herbal-cooling-face-mist/
LOCATION:Onsite at Duke Gardens – directions to follow
CATEGORIES:Adult Programs
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://gardens.duke.edu/wp-content/uploads/HG_LSullivan_1284_060623_Rose-Garden_Rosa_Reve_d-Or_Roney-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
