DESCRIPTION:Start your morning with connection\, ideas\, and energy at our 
 new Triangle entrepreneur series hosted at Raleigh Founded. Each session ru
 ns from 8:30–10:30 a.m. and blends inspiring talks\, interactive mini-sessi
 ons and facilitated networking designed to spark collaboration and action. 
 With rotating themes\, such as transitions\, growth\, strategy\, storytelli
 ng and more\, you’ll leave with fresh insights\, new connections and moment
 um to fuel your business and your day.\n\nFree parking is available for thi
 s event. Please park at the Oval West Parking Deck behind the Partners Buil
 ding 1\, and then validate your parking with your vehicle's license plate n
 umber using a QR available upon entry.
