DESCRIPTION:Paying for graduate school doesn’t have to be overwhelming. Joi
 n the Jenkins Graduate Programs and NC State's Office of Scholarships and F
 inancial Aid for an information session on financial aid for graduate stude
 nts. Morgan Middleton\, senior assistant director in the Office of Scholars
 hips and Financial Aid\, will lead the session. Morgan will cover financial
  aid options available to graduate students\, including scholarships\, loan
 s\, employer sponsorships and other funding resources. He will also provide
  tips for planning and managing the cost of your degree. Whether you’re exp
 loring graduate programs or preparing to enroll\, this session will help yo
 u understand your funding options and make informed decisions about investi
 ng in your education.
