DESCRIPTION:Link to join: https://www.mobilize.us/join/48393598/1:bd8ac0b19
 bbaa17477faace220d8eb97940e5a65ed7acada510fdb0535776b82/\n\n### Join Our Gr
 eater Triangle Regional Coalition Meeting\n\n- 📅 **When**: 3rd Wednesday o
 f every month\, 6:00 – 7:00 PM\n- 📍 **Where**: Virtual (Online)\n\nDemocra
 cy NC’s Greater Triangle region covers **Wake\, Harnett\, and Johnston coun
 ties.**\n\n**We come together to:**\n\n- Build strong grassroots leadership
 \n- Equip people to take action\n- Serve “the good of the whole”\n\nWhether
  you’re brand new or already engaged\, this space is for learning\, sharing
 \, and organizing for **a movement built of\, by\, and for the people**\, g
 rounded in equity\, solidarity\, and justice.\n\n**A note from your Greater
  Triangle Regional Managing Organizer:** \nI’m passionate about building co
 mmunity\, amplifying voices\, and creating spaces where people can be heard
  and find their role in supporting civic engagement and protecting our demo
 cracy. This work keeps me grounded\, and I’m excited to invite you to be pa
 rt of it.\n\n**Join us\, share your voice\, and help shape the work ahead!*
 *\n\nHow to prepare:\nThank you for signing up to attend our monthly coalit
 ion meeting!\n\nEach month\, you’ll get a reminder with details on what we’
 ll be discussing and the actions we can take together. We’re excited to sta
 y connected and work alongside you to make an impact.\n\nHope to see you on
 line!\n\n— Sugelema Lynch\n\nhttps://www.mobilize.us/democracync/event/8964
 13/
LAST-MODIFIED:20260206T014222Z
LOCATION:Virtual event
SEQUENCE:0
