DESCRIPTION:Join NC State Industry Expansion Solutions for a webinar on Hos
 hin Kanri\, the method that connects long-term vision with daily execution.
  You’ll discover how to set and prioritize breakthrough goals\, translate t
 hem into annual targets and engage all levels of the organization in achiev
 ing them. This webinar will provide managers and lean professionals with pr
 actical tools and insights to strengthen their strategy deployment and deli
 ver sustainable results.
