X-SOURCE-ID:nc_cultural_resources
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Celebrations & Commemorations,Reenactments & Living History
DESCRIPTION:Take a turn about our Historic Garden and enjoy the sights and 
 scents that our Founding Fathers also enjoyed. Our costumed interpreters wi
 ll also share about the variety of uses of plants during the American Revol
 ution and their use today. FREE. All ages welcome. Drop-in.
