DESCRIPTION:Join us at Fort Fisher State Historic Site this spring for our 
 annual event about Civil War artillery on May 30th\, 2026!\n\nGeneral admis
 sion is FREE\, no tickets required for entry. Doors open at 9:00am and clos
 e at 5:00pm. Public programs will be held between 10:00am and 4:00pm.\n\nMo
 re information about these programs will be provided in the coming months. 
 Stay tuned to the NC DNCR Events Calendar and Fort Fisher's social media as
  we approach May 30!
