BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"NC Cultural Resources": "https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/nc-trail-days-2026"}
X-SOURCE-ID:nc_cultural_resources
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Exhibits & Tours,Exhibitions,Organizational,Volunteer Opportunit
 ies,Performances & Arts,Concerts (Music),Education Programs,Lectures & Talk
 s,Panels & Book Discussions,Celebrations & Commemorations,Festivals & Fairs
 ,Parades & Community Celebrations,Reenactments & Living History,Guided Tour
 s,Outdoor & Recreation,Outdoor Recreation (kayak, paddle, hikes),Nature & W
 ildlife Programs,Youth & Family Activities
DESCRIPTION:NC Trail Days returns to the towns of Elkin and Jonesville\, No
 rth Carolina on the first weekend of June. This four day event celebrates t
 he 'Great Trails State' along with the abundant opportunities for outdoor r
 ecreation in this part of the Blue Ridge foothills. The event features an a
 rray of guided hikes\, several of which are along the NC Mountains-to-Sea T
 rail and the Overmountain Victory National Historic Trail\, as well as mult
 iple paddle trips on the Yadkin River. Many of the hikes are themed and foc
 us on unique regional history such as the popular hidden moonshine stills h
 ike\, or the naturalist hiking series which offers glimpses of the area's e
 cology and milltown history. In addition to guided and self-guided hikes\, 
 the festival offers rock climbing at nearby Stone Mountain and Pilot Mounta
 in State Parks\, cycling\, trail races\, outdoor gear vendors\, live music 
 and more. Nearly all the events are free to attend but may require registra
 tion. These details will be released with the schedule in Spring of 2026. C
 heck out www.nctraildays.com for more info until then\, and we hope to see 
 you there!
DTEND:20260605T040000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022459Z
DTSTART:20260604T120000Z
GEO:36.242597;-80.851612
LOCATION:Yadkin Valley Heritage & Trails Visitor Center
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:NC Trail Days 2026
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52135880677843
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/nc-trail-days-2026
END:VEVENT
