X-SOURCE-URLS:{"NC State University": "https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/new-sba-7a-manufacturers-access-to-revolving-credit-marc-loans-webinar"}
X-SOURCE-ID:ncsu
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Training
DESCRIPTION:Join NC State Industry Expansion Solutions for a webinar that w
 ill focus on the Small Business Administration's (SBA) new 7(a) Manufacture
 rs’ Access to Revolving Credit (MARC) Loans.\n\nMARC is SBA’s first-ever lo
 an program dedicated to supporting America’s small manufacturers\, which ma
 ke up 98% of all U.S. manufacturers. The program will offer working capital
  for small businesses engaged in manufacturing and is specifically designed
  to provide maximum flexibility and minimal red tape.\n\nMARC complements t
 he SBA’s core 7(a) and 504 loan programs\, providing a flexible new line of
  credit to manufacturers and lenders. MARC loans can be used in combination
  with SBA and conventional commercial loans\, making it a potent new tool i
 n support of SBA's effort to reshore American industrial dominance.
DTEND:20260611T150000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022452Z
DTSTART:20260611T140000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY: Webinar: 7(a) Manufacturers’ Access to Revolving Credit Loans
