DESCRIPTION:Please join us for the June meeting of the America 250 NC Virtu
 al Book Club! We will be discussing Tobacco Wives by Adele Myers on June 17
 th at 6p.\n\nThis historical fiction novel is set in 1940s North Carolina\,
  when a young woman discovers dangerous secrets about big tobacco...all in 
 a town that relies on a tobacco economy. \n\nPlease read the book prior to 
 the discussion. We recommend borrowing from your local library. \n\nFree an
 d open to the public. No membership required. Come to whichever book talks 
 spark your interest. \n\nMeeting Link\n\nMore Information\n\nSign up for an
  Email Reminder
