BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"NC State University": "https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/become-a-certified-bike-safety-leader"}
X-SOURCE-ID:ncsu
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Training,Community Events
DESCRIPTION:NC State Transportation is thrilled to host a three-day League 
 Cycling Instructor (LCI) Seminar from June 19 to June 21\, led by experienc
 ed League Cycling Coach Leta Highsmith. This intensive training empowers pr
 ospective educators to master the League of American Bicyclists’ Smart Cycl
 ing curriculum\, preparing them to teach riders of all ages to navigate tra
 ffic confidently\, handle their bikes safely and ride legally.\n\nParticipa
 nts must complete the Smart Cycling Complete class and purchase an individu
 al League of American Bicyclists membership as prerequisites for the class.
 \n\nSpaces are limited\, so please register by May 21 to secure your spot f
 or the seminar. Visit the NC State Transportation webpage for more informat
 ion or contact Demar Bonnemere at demar_bonnemere@ncsu.edu  with any questi
 ons.
DTEND:20260620T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022452Z
DTSTART:20260619T210000Z
GEO:35.78772;-78.683365
LOCATION:Administrative Services I\, 1117
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Become a Certified Bike Safety Leader
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52056153226589
URL:https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/become-a-certified-bike-safety-leader
END:VEVENT
