DESCRIPTION:How did North Carolinians keep crime down and conduct legal mat
 ters in the backcountry? John Haley was a tax collector and sheriff - what 
 was work like? Join our costumed interpreters as they talk about how 18th c
 entury society was policed and how laws were kept. FREE. All ages welcome. 
 Drop-in.
