CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Lectures & Talks,Exhibits & Tours,Guided Tour
 s
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a tour of the Moravian Archives Vault featuring the
  collection materials from the Revolutionary War and early American History
 !\n\nGuests will walk through the Archives Vault which contains millions of
  records from the settlement of the Moravians here in North Carolina in the
  1750s on. Highlighted items will include correspondence from George Washin
 gton\, the Fourth of July Proclamation\, maps\, congressional records and m
 uch\, much more!\n\nLearn about Moravian History and the creation of our na
 tion while seeing how such collection materials are preserved for our poste
 rity!
DTEND:20260625T183000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022459Z
DTSTART:20260625T170000Z
LOCATION:The Archie K. Davis Center 
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Tours of the Moravian Archives Vault--America 250 Theme
