DESCRIPTION:The Avery County Heritage Festival commemorates the history and
  heritage of our county including the genealogies of our Avery County famil
 ies.  Traditional craftsmen will demonstrate pioneer life.  Entertainment i
 s provided by local musicians playing traditional bluegrass and gospel sele
 ctions.  Food and craft vendors will be onsite also.
