BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"NC Cultural Resources": "https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/chatham-celebrates-america-250-cumulative-celebration"}
X-SOURCE-ID:nc_cultural_resources
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Celebrations & Commemorations,Festivals & Fairs
DESCRIPTION:July 4\, 2026\, marks 250 years since the signing of the Declar
 ation of Independence. Join Chatham Celebrates America 250 in recognizing t
 he Semiquincentennial during our\n\nJuly 4\, 2026\, marks 250 years since t
 he signing of the Declaration of Independence. Join Chatham Celebrates Amer
 ica 250 in recognizing the Semiquincentennial during our Cumulative Celebra
 tion on Sat\, Jun 27\, 2026\, 10am-2pm. Admission is free. Together\, we’ll
  remember the events that have shaped our history\, reflect on the present\
 , and envision a promising future for the next generation.\n\nFestivities w
 ill include live music and performances\, food trucks\, vendors\, displays 
 and demonstrations\, activities for children\, and much more. If you are in
 terested in participating\, volunteering\, or getting involved in other way
 s\, please contact Lindsay Ray at lindsay.ray@chathamcountync.gov or 919.54
 5.8302.\n\nThis free\, family-friendly event takes place indoors at the Cha
 tham County Agriculture & Conference Center (CCACC). Shuttle services will 
 be provided by Chatham Transit. CCACC is an ADA-compliant space\, featuring
  wheelchair-accessible parking\, entrances\, shared spaces\, and walkways. 
 Since most of the festivities will take place indoors\, this event will not
  be pet-friendly. Please leave your furry friends at home. Service animals 
 are welcome.\n\nSee more America 250 events. Learn more on the Chatham Cele
 brates America 250 Microsite. See more events at the Chatham County Agricul
 ture & Conference Center.\n\nAmerica 250 NC is North Carolina's commemorati
 on planning organization responsible for leading the initiative and collabo
 rating with various local\, state\, and federal partners.
DTEND:20260627T180000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022459Z
DTSTART:20260627T140000Z
GEO:35.723781;-79.196709
LOCATION:Chatham County Agriculture & Conference Center
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Chatham Celebrates America 250: Cumulative Celebration
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51806812854108
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/chatham-celebrates-america-250-cumulat
 ive-celebration
END:VEVENT
