DESCRIPTION:Welcome Spectators!\n\nFriday & Saturday July 3rd & 4th\, the A
 JSA is bringing back Jet Ski Racing to Isothermal Community College!\n\nWe 
 hope you'll come out to experience the thrilling action of jet ski racing\,
  aka water cross. You will see racers from the age of 8 through 70 on both 
 stand up and sit-down watercraft.\n\n \n\nWelcome Pro racers from around th
 e country as well as a freestyle exhibition where you will see jet ski's fl
 ipping on flat water!\n\nCome hungry as there will be vendors providing BBQ
 \, tacos\, nachos\, pizza\, funnel cakes\, homemade lemonade\, icees and sn
 ow cones.\n\n \n\nThere will also be crafts\, and AJSA merchandise.\n\n \n\
 nBe sure to bring a lawn chair
