X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Lectures & Talks
DESCRIPTION:Have you heard of the Tory War? From 1780-81\, Cumberland Count
 y and the surrounding region fell into a civil war between Tories and Patri
 ots during the American Revolution. Learn the stories of courage and horror
  that took place in this formative period in the region's history!
DTEND:20260725T180000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022500Z
DTSTART:20260725T170000Z
