X-SOURCE-URLS:{"NC Cultural Resources": "https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/dune-ranger-discovery-camp-8318"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"NC Cultural Resources": "https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/dune-ranger-discovery-camp"}
X-SOURCE-ID:nc_cultural_resources
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Outdoor & Recreation,Nature & Wildlife Progra
 ms
DESCRIPTION:Calling all future Dune Rangers!  Join Ranger Austin and friend
 s for a fun\, educational\, and adventurous three-day camp.  Explore mariti
 me forests\, paddle on the Roanoke Sound\, climb the tallest active dune on
  the east coast\, be creative with cool arts and crafts projects\, play goo
 fy games\, help with stewardship projects\, and make new friends.  At the e
 nd of the week\, you will be an official Dune Ranger!  Our camp is supporte
 d by Friends of Jockey’s Ridge.  \n\nJuly 29 - July 31\, 2026       9:00am 
 to 12:00pm daily\n\nOpen to grades 3-6.\n\nPre-registration is required.  P
 lease email austin.paul@ncparks.gov to signup.  \n\nThe mission of the Dune
  Ranger Discovery Camp will focus on the following elements.\n\nProvide edu
 cational opportunities for our youth (both local and visitors)\,\n\nto prom
 ote stewardship and an appreciation for our natural areas\,\n\nto provide a
  safe place for our youth to interact with others and create friendships\,\
 n\nto promote an active lifestyle\,\n\nallow for creativity\,\n\nand to hav
 e fun.
DTEND:20260729T160000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022500Z
DTSTART:20260729T130000Z
GEO:35.963597;-75.632255
LOCATION:Jockey's Ridge State Park
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Dune Ranger Discovery Camp 
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52003144711621
URL:https://events.dncr.nc.gov/event/dune-ranger-discovery-camp
END:VEVENT
