DESCRIPTION:QRSI 2026 (Qualitative Research Summer Intensive) from Research
 Talk is a premier\, week-long training program for researchers\, co-hosted 
 with UNC's Odum Institute\, offering intensive\, expert-led courses in qual
 itative research methods\, theory\, and data analysis\, with options for fo
 undational to advanced topics\, including using AI\, grounded theory\, and 
 developing practical skills for various disciplines.
