DESCRIPTION:Link to join: https://www.mobilize.us/join/46980013/1:131cbf249
 81d36476e2d699fc3297e842d6b1b0f5658afd40500bfa5279cafa0/\n\nFight Back With
  Friends! is a national program designed to help you activate your communit
 y! Using the Empower app\, the powerful relational organizing app\, we’ll e
 quip you with the tools to connect with friends\, family\, and neighbors wh
 o need YOUR voice to get civically engaged. Join us on the fourth Tuesday o
 f every month for a one-hour training session\, where we’ll onboard new par
 ticipants and introduce fresh calls to action that make a real impact.\n\nH
 ow to prepare:\nUse this link to download the Empower app and access the ca
 ll to action: https://empowerthefuture.us/Indivisible. Then\, use the invit
 e code Indivisible. \n\nBefore joining the meeting\, be sure to have your c
