DESCRIPTION:Are you a manufacturer struggling to find skilled workers to fi
 ll your open positions? If so\, look no further than veterans. These highly
  trained individuals possess unique skills and qualities that make them ide
 al candidates for careers in manufacturing. Recruiting veterans for manufac
 turing careers is a win-win situation. They bring a wealth of experience\, 
 discipline and technical skills that can significantly benefit the industry
 .\n\nNC State University Industry Expansion Solutions will host a webinar o
 n recruiting veterans for manufacturing jobs. Participants will learn about
 :\n\nThe benefits of hiring veteransMilitary workforce basicsMilitary workf
 orce impedimentsVeterans transition programsMilitary occupational specialti
 es
