 ntown Durham events in September on the third Tuesday of every month. We w
 ould love your suggestions on venues! Just ping us.\n\nQuestions or sugges
 tions?\n\nOur digital door is always open at www.downtowntechies.com or @d
 owntowntechies. Check out our events in Raleigh as well!\n\nMeet\, Drink a
 nd be TECHIE!\n\n-Jake and Blake\n\nLooking to get more connected to the l
 ocal tech scene\, opportunity or talent? Email us info@downtowntechies.com
  and we will make sure you find what you need!
