DESCRIPTION:Pearl Harbor Day and Veterans Day Remembrances\n\n \n\nOperatin
 g aboard Battleship NORTH CAROLINA\, the Azalea Coast Radio Club hosts worl
 dwide HAM radio operator events commemorating:  \n\nThe December 7\, 1941 a
 ttack on Pearl HarborVeterans DayThe Battleship is NI4BK\, and HAM operator
 s may contact the ship via Voice\, Digital\, and Morse Code. NI4BK looks fo
 rward to hearing from YOU!\n\nRadio operators making contact will receive a
  special postcard verifying the contact.
