X-SOURCE-ID:nc_cultural_resources
X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Celebrations & Commemorations,Reenactments & 
 Living History,Youth & Family Activities
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we look at Christmas traditions during the colonial 
 period in the Palmer Marsh House and into the early Victorian period in the
  Bonner House. Christmas décor of the time periods\, vignettes\, live music
 \, and light refreshments. \n\nUse of Palmer-Marsh\, Palmer Marsh yard\, Bo
 nner House and Kitchen
DTEND:20261213T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260307T022500Z
