X-SOURCE:NC Cultural Resources
CATEGORIES:Education Programs,Lectures & Talks,Outdoor & Recreation,Nature 
 & Wildlife Programs
DESCRIPTION:Become more Bear Wise and learn all about black bears physical 
 features\, behavioral patterns\, and how they change with age. We will also
  learn about prevention methods for both backcountry and rural settings\, a
 longside what to do if you encounter a bear in either setting. The Black Be
 ar program will be held at The Seven Devils Community Center as part of the
 ir Ranger Workshop Series.
